name: Vans Classic Slip-On Shoe
description:
VANS CLASSIC SLIP-ON SHOE

The Vans Classic Slip-On Shoe is arguably the most iconic piece of footwear to ever emerge from contemporary skate/surf culture. Featuring a minimal low-profile design, elastic side accents, and a classic upper pattern, the Classic is likely to still be around long after your skating days, so you may as well get those miles in.

FEATURES

A (literal) Classic slip-on street shoe
Rubber waffle grips concrete for casual cruising
Elastic side accents slip on easy—for chill time

name: Vans Ultrarange Rapidweld Shoe
description:
VANS ULTRARANGE RAPIDWELD SHOE

A new addition to the Vans family, the athlete-inspired UltraRange Rapidweld was the solution to Van's top surfers' need for a versatile shoe that provided comfort for long journeys around the world. Featuring a brand new UltraCush Lite midsole compound offering the ultimate in comfort and durability, plus a LuxLiner sock-fit construction with seamless internals to reduce weight, rubbing, and hotspots, the UltraRange Rapidweld provides a clean aesthetic that will get you there. It also includes synthetic, textile, and suede uppers, fully breathable mesh with Rapidweld details, water-based inks and glues, Pro Vulc Lite construction, and durable rubber reverse waffle lug outsoles.

name: Oofos Ooriginal Sandal
description:
OOFOS OORIGINAL SANDAL

The OOFOS story begins with the OOriginal Sandal. This combination of sleek design and revolutionary OOfoam recovery technology lays the groundwork for all future styles and models.

Revolutionary OOfoam technology absorbs 37% more impact than traditional footwear foam materials to reduce the stress on your feet and joints.

FEATURES

OOfoam technology absorbs 37% more impact than traditional footwear.
Proprietary footbed design reduces stress on knees, ankles and other joints.
Closed-cell foam is machine washable and designed to minimize odor.

name: Chaco Lowdown Sandal - Women's
description:
CHACO LOWDOWN SANDAL - WOMEN'S

Meet the Lowdown, Chaco’s lightweight, low-profile sport sandal built for a travel-ready life on the go. Featuring just the essentials, like their iconic Z/Straps with cinch buckle for a truly customized fit, plus pull-through adjustment in the heel riser to maximize barefoot comfort. The Lowdown Sandal looks great dressed up or down and is engineered with high-rebound EVA and the contoured LUVSEAT arch-support for healthy alignment and all-day comfort underfoot. Vegan. Easy to clean.

FEATURES

Chacogrip: Upgraded rubber compound with new tread designs, optimized for wet traction.
The Luvseat footbed boasts durable and long lasting all-day comfort and support certified by podiatrists.
Low profile design is 40% lighter than their classic sport sandals.
Durable and long lasting for all-day wear
3.0 MM lug outsole for no slip traction.

TECH SPECS

UPPER

Adjustable polyester jacquard webbing with injection molded ladder lock buckle and synthetic trims

MIDSOLE

Signature LUVSEAT footbed for all-day support and comfort
Vegan-friendly construction

OUTSOLE

Non-marking ChacoGrip rubber compound
3.0mm lug depth

Every pair comes standard with adjustable straps that custom-fits to your foot, plus the podiatrist-certified LUVSEAT PU footbed for all-day comfort and support. name: Salomon Speedcross 6 Gore-Tex Trail Running Shoe - Women's

breadcrumbs.name: Salomon Speedcross 6 Gore-Tex Trail Running Shoe - Women's

description:
SALOMON SPEEDCROSS 6 GORE-TEX TRAIL RUNNING SHOE - WOMEN'S

SPEEDCROSS 6 GORE-TEX needs no introductions. True to its legendary roots and trail icon status, this version is lighter with an even more powerful, grippy connection to the ground and faster mud evacuation. Featuring a waterproof and breathable Gore-Tex membrane ideal for wet and muddy conditions, a revamped upper and classic SPEEDCROSS comfort.

Grip
An updated outsole means these Speedcross shed the mud quicker and deliver an even better grip on wet surfaces.

Fit
Featuring Sensifit construction for precise, optimal foothold, and classic Speedcross comfort.

Gore-Tex
A waterproof, and breathable Gore-Tex membrane to keep your feet dry and comfortable even in tough, muddy conditions.

Mud Contagrip
Built for maximum grip on loose, soft, rugged, and uneven surfaces, Mud Contagrip uses deep, sharp lugs made from a compound that focuses on adhesion.

EnergyCell+
EnergyCell+ is a high-rebound midsole compound that provides exceptional energy return along with substantial cushioning and durability.

GORE-TEX
GORE-TEX keeps your feet dry -from the outside as well as from the inside.

Anti-debris Mesh
Tight mesh that prevents debris from being trapped between your foot and the footbed.

Ripstop fabric
Woven fabrics, often made of nylon, with reinforcement to resist tearing, ripping and abrasion.

Quicklace
Minimalistic and strong lace for one-pull tightening. Easy-on, easy-off.

Recycled material
Materials made from recycled products such as PET bottles or material waste

TECH SPECS

Inlay sole: Textile
Lining: Textile
Outsole: Rubber
Upper: Synthetic / Textile
Drop: 10 in mm
Lug depth: 5 mm
Heel stack height: 33 mm
Forefoot stack height: 23 mm
Weight: 279 g
Lacing system: Quicklace
Waterproofness: GORE-TEX

name: Teva Original Universal Sandal - Women's
description:
TEVA ORIGINAL UNIVERSAL SANDAL - WOMEN'S

From a Grand Canyon raft in 1984 to docks, stoops, and sidewalks around the world, one of Teva’s very first sandal stands as a testament to timeless comfort and utilitarian style.

FEATURES

Quick-dry webbing made from recycled plastic using traceable, verifiable REPREVE polyester yarn by Unifi, these sandals save 4 plastic bottles from ending up in landfills
The Universal Strapping System and earth-friendly recycled polyester webbing supports your foot and stands up to abuse, Multiple points of adjustability let you dial in the absolute perfect fit
Easy hook-and-loop closure comes on and off quickly and gets the fit just right

TECH SPECS

Molded EVA midsole with heel cupping and arch cookie for added support
Rubber outsole for durability and traction
Vegan footwear, created using synthetic and plant-based materials
This style is recyclable. Our TevaForever recycling program accepts any style of your well-loved Teva sandals to be recycled and they’ll never see a landfill

name: Asics GEL-NIMBUS 24 Running Shoe - Women's
description:
ASICS GEL-NIMBUS 24 RUNNING SHOE - WOMEN'S

The GEL-NIMBUS 24 shoe offers advanced impact protection for your distance training. Creating a softer landing in every step, this shoe is also approx. 10g lighter than the previous version. The upper’s soft engineered mesh and flexible midfoot panel make these shoes more comfortable during long runs. By moving seamlessly with your foot, they help your stride feel smoother in every step. FF BLAST PLUS cushioning keeps the shoe lightweight while providing a softer feeling underfoot. This material also helps increase the shoe's rebound properties at the toe-off stage.

FEATURES

Engineered mesh upper wraps the foot with a soft feel while improving breathability
Rearfoot and Forefoot GEL Technology Cushioning System - Attenuates shock during impact and toe-off phases, and allows movement in multiple planes as the foot transitions through the gait cycle.
Trusstic System technology - Reduces the weight of the sole unit while retaining the structural integrity of the shoe.
FF BLAST+ cushioning creates a softer landing and a more responsive toe-off
FLYTEFOAM cushioning provides lightweight impact absorption
OrthoLite X-55 sockliner improves step-in comfort
Reflective details improve visibility in low-light conditions
3D Space construction improves compression and cushioning at footstrike and reduces pronation
Made with recycled materials to reduce waste and carbon emissions
ASICS LITE rubber is lighter, stronger, and more sustainable than standard outsole rubbers
AHAR outsole rubber improves durability

TECH SPECS

Heel Drop: 13 mm
Weight: 247g (8.7 oz)

name: Patagonia Torrentshell 3L Jacket - Men's
description:
PATAGONIA TORRENTSHELL 3L JACKET - MEN'S

Simple and unpretentious, Patagonia's trusted Torrentshell 3L Jacket uses 3-layer H2No Performance Standard technology and a PFC-free DWR finish (durable water repellent coating that does not contain perfluorinated chemicals) for exceptional waterproof/breathable performance, all-day comfort and long-lasting waterproof durability.

FEATURES

Two-way-adjustable hood with a laminated visor that rolls down and stows with a simplified cord-and-hook design
Microfleece-lined neck provides comfort and protects with a waterproof/breathable barrier
Snag-free center-front zipper with external and internal storm flaps and zipper-garage chin guard
Two handwarmer pockets and venting pit zips with welted exterior storm flaps
Self-fabric hook-and-loop cuff closures and an adjustable drawcord hem seal out precipitation
Jacket self-stuffs into left handwarmer pocket with carabiner clip-in loop

TECH SPECS

Waterproof/breathable H2No Performance Standard 3-layer shell with a PFC-free DWR finish (durable water repellent coating that does not contain perfluorinated chemicals) provides the highest levels of comfort and performance, and long-term waterproof durability

  • Two handwarmer pockets and venting pit zips with welted exterior storm flaps
  • Self-fabric hook-and-loop cuff closures and an adjustable drawcord hem seal out precipitation
  • Jacket self-stuffs into left handwarmer pocket with carabiner clip-in loop

TECH SPECS

  • Waterproof/breathable H2No Performance Standard 3-layer shell with a PFC-free DWR finish (durable water repellent coating that does not contain perfluorinated chemicals) provides the highest levels of comfort and performance, and long-term waterproof durability

name: KÜHL Renegade Pant - Men's
description:
KÜHL RENEGADE PANT - MEN'S

Comfortable, breathable, and ready for action - the KÜHL Renegade pant. Cut from innovative DURALUX, the durable softshell fabric feels like cotton to the touch. The KÜHL Renegade Pants are strong, breathable, and have anti-abrasion and quick-dry properties to keep you cool and dry all day long. The waistband is slightly peached for increased wicking performance and faster drying. 8 Total pockets allow you to keep your important items close by and secure.

FEATURES

Waistband peached for increased wicking performance, faster drying time and unmatched comfort
Easy care, wash and wear
8 total pockets: 2 front hand, 2 back, 2 zippered side, 1 stealth cell phone, 1 3D cell phone
UPF 50
Gusseted crotch for freedom of movement
Articulated knees

TECH SPECS

Fabric: DURALUX 95% Nylon, 5% Spandex with DWR
Durable 2-way stretch fabric has great hand and dries quickly with DWR

name: The North Face Basin 24 Backpack
description:
THE NORTH FACE BASIN 24 BACKPACK

The Basin 24 is TNF's mid-sized daypack with trail-ready durability and features such as easy-access bottle stashes, a breathable back panel, and an integrated rain cover so you can go into any outdoor challenge in comfort and with confidence.

FEATURES

NextVent back panel and shoulder straps offer padding and breathability for a comfortable yet minimalist carry
Concealed rain cover deploys easily and attaches to specific points for a precise fit
Large main compartment holds your trail needs
External stash pocket holds bulky or quick-access items, and compression straps hold items in place
Minimalist, two-point trekking-pole attachment to hold poles
Two quick-access water bottle pockets
Lightweight nylon ripstop helps keep pack weight down while the rugged polyester boot provides durability where you need it
Sternum strap with a whistle buckle
Hydration sleeve (Hydration System not included)

TECH SPECS

Body: 210D recycled nylon ripstop with non-PFC durable water-repellent (non-PFC DWR) finish
Avg Weight: 1 lb 7 oz (695 g)
Boot: 600D recycled polyester
Dimensions: 11'' x 6.7'' x 19.7'' (27.9 cm x 17 cm x 50 cm)
Volume: 1465 in³ (24 liters)

description:
UNDER ARMOUR HARPER 7 MID RM BASEBALL CLEAT - BOYS'

The Under Armour Harper 7 Mid RM Baseball Cleat is designed to provide your young baseball player with comfort, stability, and traction. The synthetic upper is lightweight and breathable, while molded detailing offers added support. The molded 4D foam footbed provides extra cushioning and a custom fit, while the full-length Micro G midsole enhances responsiveness. The rubber outsole provides excellent traction on the diamond, and the cleat's mid-top design provides extra ankle support. Perfect for any young player, the Under Armour Harper 7 Mid RM Baseball Cleat is a great choice.

Full-length EVA midsole for underfoot cushion & comfort
Rubber molded cleats provide optimal traction & durability for all field surfaces

name: Lifetime Daylite 8' Kayak
description:
LIFETIME DAYLITE 8' SIT-ON-TOP KAYAK

Lifetime Daylite Kayak - The 8 ft. adult kayak has a 250 lb. weight capacity and comes in aqua with an adjustable backrest and one paddle (1169412). Individually packaged. 5-year limited warranty. The 8 ft. Lifetime Daylite Kayak has a comfortable backrest perfect for long kayaking adventures. Its compact design easily fits inside the average apartment or home closet, and the back end allows the kayak to stand upright. With additional features like a tankwell storage with secure bungees, a stable hull design, and UV-protected construction, the standard Daylite is transformed into the “do it all” kayak. From paddling to fishing, the Daylite is perfect for your outdoor adventure.

FEATURES

Adjustable Quick Release Seat Back for Comfort
Center Carry Handle for Easy Transport to Waterfront
Front and Rear T-Handles for Easy Transport
Hull Design Provides Ultra Stability and Great Tracking
Kayak Paddle Included
Molded Paddle Cradle
Multiple Footrest Positions for Different Size Paddlers
Paddle Included
Self-Bailing Scupper Holes to Drain Water from the Cockpit and Tankwell
Tankwell Storage with Bungee Cord Lacing to Secure Loose Items
UV-Protected High-Density Polyethylene Construction

TECH SPECS

Draft: 3 in. (7,62 cm).
Hull Material: High-Density Polyethylene (HDPE).
Length: 8 ft. (244 cm).
Maximum Weight Capacity: 250 lb. (113,4 kg).
Paddle Length: 86.6 in. (220 cm).
Paddle Materials: Molded Polymer and Aircraft Grade Aluminum.
Warranty: 5-Year Limited.
Weight: 38 lb. (17,2 kg).
Width: 30 in. (76,2 cm).

name: Brooks Hyperion Tempo Running Shoe - Women's

breadcrumbs.name: Brooks Hyperion Tempo Running Shoe - Women's

description:
BROOKS HYPERION TEMPO RUNNING SHOE - WOMEN'S

If the extra mile is calling your name, it’s time for a lightweight running shoe that matches your ambition. Brooks built the Hyperion Tempo to help you train harder and longer, all while staying comfortable through a soft, responsive midsole.

FEATURES

Ultralight Cushioning

DNA FLASH foam is nitrogen infused for an optimal combination of energy return and light weight that adapts to your unique stride and allows you to run fast

DNA FLASH is engineered from ultra-lightweight materials so none of this weighs you down.
Brooks cushioning technologies all start with DNA because they react to your unique stride.

Quick recovery

The combination of light weight, a responsive ride, and soft cushioning helps the shoe absorb impact during a hard workout — allowing you to quickly get back to the grind.

Performance fit

The breathable stretch-woven upper moves with your foot to provide maximum comfort. This helps keep your feet at a cool temperature even on hot days.

TECH SPECS

Experience: Speed
Surface: Road
Support: Neutral
Midsole drop: 8mm
Weight: 6.7oz / 189.9g
Fit: Classic Fit

name: Dakine School Case
description:
DAKINE SCHOOL CASE

The School Case rounds up all your loose writing and learning utensils into one handy zippered compartment. It's also great for managing cables, chargers-basically any of the loose stuff that you spend way too much time searching for in your bag.

FEATURES

Pencil organizer
Interior zippered pocket

Materials

AI AQUA: 400D nylon plain weave with water repellent finish
ALOHA CAMO: 600D recycled polyester plain weave with print and water repellent finish
BLACK: 600D polyester plain weave with water repellent finish
CARBON: 900D polyester heather plain weave with water repellent finish
CRESCENT FLORAL: 600D recycled polyester plain weave with print and water repellent finish
DESERT SAGE: 1000D polyester heavyweight canvas with wax finish
ELEPHANT: 600D recycled polyester plain weave with water repellent finish / 600D recycled polyester plain weave with print and water repellent finish
FLASH REFLECTIVE: 600D recycled polyester plain weave with reflective print and water repellent finish
GREYSCALE: 300D polyester heather plain weave with water repellent finish / 400D nylon + polyester heather plain weave with water repellent finish
MINI TROPICAL: 600D recycled polyester plain weave with print and water repellent finish / 510D heather plain weave with water repellent finish
ORCHID: 600D recycled polyester plain weave with print and water repellent finish
PINEAPPLE: 600D recycled polyester plain weave with print and water repellent finish
SPARROW: 600D cotton + polyester plain weave with water repellent finish
SUN FLARE: 200D nylon twill weave with water repellent finish
TWILIGHT FLORAL: 600D recycled polyester plain weave with print and water repellent finish

Care Instructions

If your Dakine bag gets dirty, Dakine recommends hand washing with mild soap (like Nikwax Tech Wash), cold water and a soft bristle brush. If hand washing is not going to do the trick, use a front loader washing machine. To ensure your backpack doesn't get tangled, place inside a pillowcase or mesh bag before washing. Always use cold water, mild soap and run on a gentle cycle. Never bleach your pack. Hang to dry in a warm but shady place, ensuring both inside and out are dry before storing.

name: Exped Radical 45 Duffel Backpack
description:
EXPED RADICAL DUFFEL 45

Whether you're heading to campus, work, the gym, or the airport, the 2700+ cubic inch-capacity Exped Radical 45 duffel is a burly carry-all bag designed to haul gear and clothing with smart organizational features. The padded design and water-resistant construction protect the contents and make it easy to carry wherever your journey takes you.

The duffel's backpanel and shoulder straps have thick padding for a comfortable backpack carry no matter what gear you're hauling. The straps also convert to allow for shoulder carry and can be safely stowed away when not needed. An adjustable sternum strap and webbing hipbelt provide additional support if you need to hike to your destination, and both can be removed for a more streamlined look.

The weather-protected main compartment is accessed through long, beefy zipper down the main back panel. Inside, internal climbing rack loops double as attachment loops for other types of gear. There are two large side pockets, one with a water repellent liner that can be used to store sweaty or damp clothes, and one with mesh material, a key clip, and internal access to the main compartment. On the outside, compression straps at either end allow you to attach gear externally or cinch down the pack when it's not full.

The main body of the duffel utilizes 210D recycled Robic HD ripstop nylon and 600D recycled polyester, and the lining is 150D recycled polyester. All of the fabrics have a PU coating, so while the pack is not fully waterproof, it does offer excellent weather-resistance and the tough outer fabrics grant long-lived durability.

FEATURES

Fully padded bag for easy packing and to protect contents
Main zipper is long and burly for easy access and packing
Carrying comfort with padded back and beefy shoulder straps
Easy organization with large, practical pockets
Internal rack loops also serve as practical attachment loops for just about anything (keys, belt pouches etc)
Two large side pockets including one with a key clip, mesh material, and direct access to the main compartment and one with a water repellent liner to store sweaty sportswear
Upper and lower compression straps
Shoulder straps are easily stowed in the side pockets or can be lengthened and used as a carry-on shoulder strap
Aluminum toggle system for strap adjustment
Reflective logo print

TECH SPECS

Item Dimensions: 25.2" x 13.4" x 9.1"
Maximum Weight: 28 lbs
Volume: 2624 cu in
Item Weight: 29.3 oz

name: Coleman Blue Springs II 8-Person Camping Tent

breadcrumbs.name: Coleman Blue Springs II 8-Person Camping Tent

description:
COLEMAN BLUE SPRINGS II 8-PERSON CAMPING TENT

Gather the gang for good times in the great outdoors. Coleman tents, like our spacious Blue Springs II 8-person tent are designed to make it happen. Comfy campers are happy campers, so our Weathertec system helps keep water out with a tub-style floor, welded corners, inverted seams, taped seams, and a tough fiberglass frame that's wind-tested up to 35 mph. When you need a little personal space, a room divider provides extra privacy, and the wide door on this spacious tent makes it easy to get airbeds and other large gear in and out. Easy setup means you relax more and stress less, so this model also boasts snag-free continuous pole sleeves. And you’ll catch every breeze with an advanced ventilation system that includes a mesh roof, rainfly with awning, and a ground vent. This large camping tent measures 17’ x 10‘ x 6’ and is roomy enough to fit 3 queen-size airbeds, meanwhile two gear pockets help keep smaller items from getting lost. Durable polyester body, fiberglass poles, and polyethylene floor. 1-year limited warranty.

FEATURES

Room divider adds extra privacy
Wide door allows easy access for airbeds and large gear
Snag-free continuous pole sleeves make setup easy
Mesh roof with awning and a ground vent improve airflow
Gear pockets keep smaller items at hand

TECH SPECS

WEATHERTEC PROTECTION: Tub-like floor, welded corners, inverted seams and taped seams on the rainfly and tent body help keep water out; frame has been tested to withstand winds up to 35 mph

breadcrumbs.name: Smith Optics Wilder Jr. Helmet w/ MIPS - Youth

description:
SMITH OPTICS WILDER JR. HELMET W/ MIPS

When your young rider is dedicated to the dirt, you need gear that keeps pace with their skill set. The Smith Wilder Jr. mountain bike helmet combines the enhanced angle impact protection of MIPS with a lightweight, ventilated design just like Smith's adult helmets. 21 fixed vents keep the air flowing as kids bomb down their favorite trails. The VaporFit dial system adjusts around the head with the turn of a dial to get the right fit every time. There's a built-in visor to cut glare and integrated sunglasses storage, so kids can stow their glasses just like mom or dad.

FEATURES

Lightweight in-mold construction
MIPS Brain Protection System reduces rotational forces caused by angled impacts to the head
VaporFit dial adjustment system offers 270-degree fit adjustment with the turn of a dial
Designed for ultimate integration with Smith performance eyewear and goggles for maximum comfort, venting and storage convenience
AirEvac ventilation system integrates with Smith goggles and eyewear for fog-free lenses
20 fixed vents for consistent airflow
Integrated visor
Performance comfort lining
Lightweight, low-bulk single layer webbing

name: Stan's NoTubes Tire Sealant
description:
It works for cars, so why not bikes? Just like that fix-a-flat stuff you wonder about using, this milky goo seals small leaks and punctures, up to 1/4in. And the stuff works really well. The kit can convert most tubed tires to tubeless. And if you're already riding tubeless, it makes running low pressure and riding through thornbushes, glass gardens, and herds of goathead thorns all the safer. For those who are wondering, no the sealant doesn't freeze, doesn't alter the balance of the wheel, and can work in any kind of tubeless tire when combined with a UST or tubeless-ready rim. If you have a standard clincher wheelset, bear in mind that you'll still need to prep your wheels with a tubeless conversion kit before taking advantage of this sealant. The one-quart container can seal up to 16 tires. Tubeless 101: The Why and the How Explained.

Stan's NoTubes Tire Sealant Features:

Converts most tubed tires to tubeless
Makes running low pressure and riding through thornbushes, glass gardens, and herds of goathead thorns all the safer
Won't freeze
Won't alter the balance of the wheel
Seal up to 16 tires

name: Asics Gel-Kayano 29 Running Shoe - Women's
description:
ASICS GEL-KAYANO 29 RUNNING SHOE - WOMEN'S

The Gel - Kayano 29 shoe creates a stable running experience and a more responsive feel underfoot. Featuring a low-profile external heel counter, this piece comfortably cradles your foot with advanced rearfoot support. Asics also updated the midsole with FF BLAST PLUS cushioning. This helps keep the shoe lightweight while creating a more energized rebound in each step. A LITETRUSS stability feature is placed on the midsole’s inside angle. It’s designed to help keep your foot from rolling too far inward during your stride.

FEATURES

Engineered knit upper: Improves breathability.
Redesigned external heel counter: Helps keep the foot stable and provide a more comfortable stride.
LITETRUSS technology: Improves medial support and midfoot integrity.
3D SPACE CONSTRUCTION feature: Improves compression at footstrike.
Rearfoot GEL technology cushioning: Provides good shock absorption.
FF BLAST PLUS cushioning: Provides lightweight impact absorption and a responsive rebound.
OrthoLite X-55 sockliner: Improves comfort.
Reflective details: Improve visibility.
AHARPLUS heel plug: Improves the outsole durability.

TECH SPECS

The sockliner is produced with the solution dyeing process that reduces water usage by approximately 33% and carbon emissions by approximately 45% compared to the conventional dyeing technology
At least 50% of the shoe’s main upper material is made with recycled materials to reduce waste and carbon emissions

name: ACME Kamlooper Spoon Fishing Lure
description:
ACME KAMLOOPER SPOON FISHING LURE

*** Treble hook included with lure. ***

Casts like a bullet, travels for a country mile - Kamlooper is virtually unaffected by strong winds. The best of the spoon lures, it's perfect for catching gamefish (which gobble 80% of their prey from the bottom or in deeper feeding zones).

The high weight/profile ratio means that the Kamlooper gets down where the big ones live and eat. There is only one Kamlooper and smart fishermen know it.

SIZE DESCRIPTION TYPE OF FISH
1/8 oz. 2-4 lb. test Ideal for trout, smallmouth bass & minnow-eating gamefish.
3/16 oz. 4-8 lb. test Ideal for lite spinning & spincasting Ideal for trout, smallmouth bass, walleye & sauger.
3/8 oz. 6-10 lb. test Ideal for trout, lake trout, bass, walleye, salmon, steelhead & pike.
3/4 oz. 10-15 lb. test Ideal for trout, steelhead, salmon, pike, muskies, trophy-class brown & Dolly Varden trout.

description:
ALPS OUTDOORZ UPLAND GAME VEST X

The Upland Game Vest X is the perfect accessory for upland game hunting, and includes a bevy of innovative features. The shoulder straps are ultra thin for maximum shooting comfort, and two front shell pockets are large enough to accommodate an entire box of shells each. Two flip down gun rests are included (gun rests only available on Large size option), as well as a lightweight vented back and waist belt construction.

H2O compatible

Two radio pockets

name: Vans Old Skool Skate Shoe
description:
VANS OLD SKOOL SKATE SHOE

First known as the Vans #36, the Old Skool debuted in 1977 with a unique new addition: a random doodle drawn by founder Paul Van Doren, and originally referred to as the “jazz stripe.” Today, the famous Vans Sidestripe has become the unmistakable—and instantly recognizable—hallmark of the Vans brand. Constructed with durable suede and canvas uppers in a range of fresh colorways, the Old Skool pays homage to Vans' heritage while ensuring that this low top, lace-up shoe remains as iconic as ever. It also features re-enforced toe caps, supportive padded collars, and signature rubber waffle outsoles.

FEATURES

Skate shoes in an iconic, low-profile silhouette with classic Sidestripe detail
Uppers of canvas and suede or leather
Lace-up closure
Padded collar and footbed for added comfort, fit, and superior shock absorption
Cotton drill lining provides excellent breathability and extra comfort
Die-cut EVA insert for added support

TECH SPECS

Vulcanized construction: Slimmed-down profile offers a flexible feel
Gum rubber outsole with signature waffle tread provides superior grip and board feel
Weight: 1 lb. 2 oz.

description:
ADIDAS X SPEEDPORTAL.3 LACELESS FIRM GROUND SOCCER CLEAT

Discover the meaning of speed in cleats made in part with recycled materials.
Mind. Body. Cleat. Connected in the blink of an eye. Pull on adidas X Speedportal to unlock speed in all its dimensions. Built to fly on firm ground, these laceless soccer cleats have a lightweight, coated textile upper and two extra forefoot studs. The combination of a stretchy flat-knit collar and rigid TPU heel lock ensures you're strapped in for every sprint and sidestep.

Made with a series of recycled materials, this upper features at least 50% recycled content. This product represents just one of the solutions to help end plastic waste.

name: adidas Bravada 2.0 Shoe - Women's
description:
ADIDAS BRAVADA 2.0 SHOE - WOMEN'S

Drop into the season with the retro styling of the new Bravada 2.0 Athletic Shoe by Adidas. This skate-inspired sneaker rocks sturdy canvas uppers with Cloudfoam cushioning for comfort and a vulcanzied sole for flexible traction.

Look bold, feel comfortable. Adidas Bravada 2.0 Womens Skateboarding Shoes are a stylish and supportive must-have for dressing to impress, no matter the occasion. The canvas upper is not only comfortable, but also features a unique faux vulcanised tooling detail that bucks trends while creating an on-trend silhouette. Along with a rubber toe guard and classic three stripes, this helps you add a sense of skater-style sophistication to any look. Plus, you’ll love the fact that the cotton yarns used in the making of this product support more sustainable cotton farming - for guilt-free fashion style! Perfect for days when you want to be noticed, these skate shoes give you an effortless yet fashionable feet first finish.

FEATURES

Casual athletic sneakers
Lace closure seals the fit
Cushioned collar
Textile upper is breathable and durable
Cloud foam comfort sock liner
Rubber outsole
Textile Upper, Rubber Sole

name: Osprey Transporter 40L Wheeled Duffel Bag
description:
OSPREY TRANSPORTER 40L WHEELED DUFFEL BAG

Organize and protect smaller gear items or clothes, great for a weekend abroad or in the dirt. The carry-on sized Transporter® Wheeled Duffel 40 will keep your gear and clothing safe and sound on any trip. The HighRoad Chassis features a sturdy, lightweight aluminum frame with an extendable handle and oversized wheels to keep you rolling smoothly. Overlapping rainflaps and weather-resistant zippers protect contents from weather, and multiple handles provide easy loading. Constructed with durable, TPU-coated bluesign® approved recycled polyester with a PFC-free DWR coating that sheds moisture.

FEATURES

Rugged HighRoad Chassis, dual-sided TPU coating, burly hardware, oversized flap and design details that protect your gear from external elements.
A rugged chassis with large wheels for a smooth roll over any surface: cobblestone streets, gravel roads, carpeted airport terminals or icy sidewalks.
A workhorse duffel with a carry system that won't weigh you down, no matter the load.
Wide, easy-to-pack main access
#10 YKK zippers with lockable sliders and rain flap protection
Large external end pocket keeps smaller items accessible
Four padded tubular web grab handles, plus a bottom molded foot, make the bag easy to lift from any angle
Six additional lash points ensure secure transport on a roof rack or pack animal
A large internal zippered mesh pocket help organize contents
Two internal compression straps secure load
ID window on end panel

TECH SPECS

Weight: 6lbs
Dimensions: 23.62H X 14.17W X 11.02D IN.

name: Oakley Fall Line M Goggle
description:
OAKLEY FALL LINE M GOGGLE

In skiing and snowboarding, taking the Fall Line refers to the line down a mountain that is most directly downhill. Inspired by Line Miner and fusing the large field of view from a rimless goggle, Fall Line M is the latest addition to Oakley’s “LINE SERIES” of cylindrical style snow goggles. With a mid-sized fit, Fall Line M is optimized for a wide variety of faces and is engineered to fit perfectly with most helmets. Designed with Oakley’s Ridgelock Technology, changing lenses is quick and easy while still allowing for a complete lens seal to prevent harsh conditions from penetrating into your goggle.

FEATURES

Available in Prizm Lens Technology options
Fit: Medium
Microbag included for storage and lens cleaning
Ridgelock Lens Change System
Discreet frame notches at temples provide compatibility with most prescription eyewear
Wide 40mm wide adjustable strap with silicone lining for a more secure fit
Flexible O Matter chassis conforms to your face comfortably, even in extreme cold
Rimless frame design provides increased visibility and improved helmet compatibility
All-day comfort of triple-layer face foam with moisture wicking polar fleece lining
Injection-molded Plutonite lens material provides 100% protection against UVA / UVB / UVC & harmful blue light up to 400nm
Optically correct Dual Lens with F3 Anti-fog coating
Glare reduction and tuned light transmission of Iridium lens coating (optional)
Meets impact requirements based upon ANSI Z87.1, EN 174, and ISO 18527-1

name: Cotopaxi Allpa 35L Travel Pack
description:
COTOPAXI ALLPA 35L TRAVEL PACK

The Allpa 35L’s shell is made from a blend of tough, TPU-coated 1000D polyester, with durable 840D ballistic nylon paneling. Cotopaxi adopted the low-profile harness they use for their backpacking packs to create a suspension system that distributes weight and keeps you comfortable through journeys near or far. The system includes contoured shoulder straps for comfort and balance, plus a removable hip belt you can take off when you don’t need it, or for when you’re stowing the pack in tight compartments. A breathable, flexible airmesh back panel and an adjustable sternum strap create an even more comfortable carry. There’s a suitcase-style, full-wrap zipper opening on the main compartment that opens into a large, zippered mesh compartment on the right side and a subdivided zippered mesh compartment on the left. These compartments open outward for easy and organized packing, and now feature an updated zipper gusset to create dynamic compression. This compression makes it easier to zip your Allpa closed when it’s packed tight. Two zippered pockets round out the top.

Padded laptop and tablet sleeves are accessible via the exterior right-side zipper. On the left side, there’s a shortcut zipper that provides access to the main internal compartment, without having to take the pack off your back. A subdivided compartment on the top is designed with passports and other small essentials in mind.

As a security measure, all external zippers feature our theft-proof webbing sewn across the openings. A slotted back panel houses the shoulder straps, ensuring loose ends are a non-issue in overhead bins, on the bus, or in the trunk of cars. Additionally, four reinforced grab handles provide multiple carry points when the shoulder straps are tucked away, and four lash points at the top of the pack allow you to carry more gear. There’s even a rain cover that stows into the pack.

FEATURES

Weight-distributing, low-profile harness system
Removable waist belt for simple stowage in tight compartments
Carry-on-compatible 35L capacity
TPU-coated 1000D polyester
Lighter weight, more durable 840D ballistic nylon paneling
Suitcase-style, full-wrap zipper opening on the main compartment
Large zippered mesh compartment on the right side
Subdivided zippered mesh compartment on the left side
Padded laptop and tablet sleeve for easy + secure tech storage
Shortcut zipper to main compartment so you can access your stuff in tight quarters
Top zippered pocket ideal for small travel essentials, like your wallet and passport
Security YKK zippers keep your focus on the adventure at hand
Four carabiner lash loops to haul more gear
Tuck-away shoulder straps
Four reinforced grab handles
Included rain cover
* Please note that we do not take color requests.

TECH SPECS

Weight: 3lb 8oz (1605g) / with accessories: 4lb 10oz (2100g)
Dimensions: 20 x 12 x 8in (51 x 30 x 20cm)
Volume: 35L (2136cu in)
*Please note that certain color options are an assorted item. The images shown above do not reflect the color of the product you will receive.

name: Good Sport Smashnet
description:
GOOD SPORT SMASHNET

SmashNet is played to 11 points with the objective of defending your side with only three hits. Players divide into two teams and take turns serving diagonally to the opposing player, where they must return the ball over the net in three alternating hits or less. If the ball lands on your side or it takes more than three hits to get it over, you’re out. The team that gets to 11 points first wins!

FEATURES

Custom game modes - Create and customize your own game modes with varying rules and objectives
Tournament Mode - Compete in tournaments with other players for rewards and bragging rights
Multiplayer Mode - Play with up to 16 players online or local
Online Leaderboards - Compete with players from all over the world and climb the online leaderboards
Character Customization - Create and customize your own character with a variety of clothing and accessories
Power Ups - Utilize power ups to gain an edge over your opponents
Training Mode - Practice your skills and hone your technique in the safety of a training session
Spectator Mode - Watch the best Smashnet players in action and learn from their techniques

TECH SPECS

Dimensions: 51.5" x 101" x 20" (inches)

name: Dakine DLX Pickup Tailgate Pad
description:
DAKINE DLX PICKUP PAD

Trailhead commute or gravity shuttle duty, no bike rack compares to the convenience of a Dakine Pickup Pad. The DLX pad fits modern tailgates with backup cameras. The large model works best on full-size tailgate designs and has tie-downs for up to seven bikes. The small fits midsize truck tailgates and has tie-downs for up to five bikes. A built-in security grommet lets you lock it to your truck. We've stiffened the ends of the webbing straps for easy installation under the tailgate and added cam-action buckles for quick removal.

FEATURES

Padded tailgate protection
Large access flap for tailgate handles and rear-view cameras
Works best on new tailgate designs
Individual bike anchor straps (7- Large; 5- Small)
Four web cinch straps
Cable lock compatible
Reflective logo

TECH SPECS

1000D Recycled Polyester with UV/weather-resistant coating

name: prAna Brion II Pant - Men's
description:
PRANA BRION II PANT - MEN'S

The men's Brion Pant II is an upgraded version of a long-time fan fave. Made with ReZion, the Earth-friendly evolution of the bestselling performance fabric, you can adventure confidently knowing there are over two decades of tried and trusted durability backing you up. How exactly did prAna upgrade it? They reinforced the back pocket with a double-needle topstitch and added additional reinforcement to the mobility gusset. The end result? A style that's tough enough for whatever you throw at it, but with a casual style perfect for everyday wear as well.

FEATURES

ReZion recycled nylon blend stretch performance fabric
Ventilated inseam gusset
5-pocket styling with mesh lining
Hidden zipper pocket at back right pocket
prAna woven label at back right pocket
Standard fit throught the hip and thigh
Straight leg opening
Abrasion resistant
4-way stretch
PFAS-free DWR (durable water repellent)
UPF 50+
bluesign approved materials

TECH SPECS

Fabric details: 95% Recycled Nylon | 5% Elastane

name: Teva Hurricane XLT2 Sandal - Men's
description:
TEVA HURRICANE XLT2 - MEN'S

Teva gave the iconic Hurricane XLT a fresh comfort upgrade, outfitting it with soft heel-strap padding and a new, modern sole featuring even better traction than ever before. Finished with Unifi recycled polyester straps.

FEATURES

Best for: Day hikes, Light hikes
Quick-dry webbing made from recycled plastic using traceable, verifiable REPREVE polyester yarn by Unifi supports your foot and stands up to abuse, these sandals save 4 plastic bottles from ending up in landfills
Injection-molded strap ends for quick and easy grip and adjustability, Easy hook-and-loop closure comes on and off quickly and gets the fit just right
A robust EVA footbed is made for all-day adventuring
Nylon shank stabilizes and supports your foot on uneven terrain
Rubber outsole for durability and traction
Vegan footwear, created using synthetic and plant-based materials
This style is recyclable. Teva's TevaForever recycling program accepts any style of your well-loved Teva sandals to be recycled and they’ll never see a landfill.

Half pair weight for size 7: 7.75oz

name: YETI Rambler Water Bottle - 26oz
description:
YETI RAMBLER 26 OZ WATER BOTTLE

The Rambler 26 oz. Bottle is the goldilocks of YETI's bottle line, just the right amount for almost any day and still fits in your backpack. With a quick twist, the TripleHaul handle comes off, exposing their shatter-resistant, dishwasher safe spout that allows for controlled gulps on the go. When it's time for a wash or refill, remove the entire cap to expose the bottle's wide mouth.

FEATURES

18/8 stainless steel
Double-wall vacuum insulation keeps cold drinks cold and hot drinks hot until the last sip
No Sweat exterior keeps your hands dry and unaffected, no matter how hot or cold the beverage inside
100% leakproof
Dishwasher safe

TECH SPECS

breadcrumbs.name: YETI Rambler 20oz Tumbler With Magslider Lid

description:
YETI RAMBLER 20OZ TUMBLER WITH MAGSLIDER LID

The Rambler is the tumbler that gets you through the day. Your morning brew stays hot, and your iced coffee will stay cold - so take your time. Kitchen-grade stainless steel with double-wall vacuum insulation will protect your drink at all costs. The entire Rambler Family, tumbler and whichever lid you put on it are dishwasher-safe for easy cleaning. The magnet on the included MagSlider Lid adds an additional barrier of protection for keeping drinks contained and preventing heat or cold from escaping.

Please note - this magnet component is not leakproof and will not prevent spills.

FEATURES

Cupholder compatible
Leak resistant
Dishwasher safe
Double-wall vacuum insulated

name: Easton Walk-Off NX Backpack
description:
EASTON WALK-OFF NX BACKPACK

The new and improved Easton Walk-Off NX Baseball Backpack gives players more convenience than ever! With new features like the patent-pending Gear Klip, ballplayers can transport more gear without any added hassle. This bag's extra-wide mouth opening provides easy access to the main compartment, so it's a breeze to store or remove almost anything. In addition, other compartments — like the two full-length bat sleeves, expandable mesh pockets, and unique hex-grid external helmet holder — help you stay organized and uncluttered. And to make sure you're comfortable, this backpack features padded back and shoulder straps and an increased zipper size. It all adds up to better comfort, better accessibility, and better durability.

FEATURES

Compartments: Main Compartment, Hex-Grid Helmet Holder, Gear Clip, Two Full Length Bat Sleeves, Expandale Mesh Pockets, Front Personal Pocket, Fence Hook
Dimensions: 21” H x 13” W x 101/2” D
Removable Panel: Removable Top Panel For Team Logo Embroidery

description:
store/product-description.title

BEAR ARCHERY SPECIAL EDITION LEGIT RTH COMPOUND BOW

The Legit's broad adjustability and incredible value has made it one of the most sought after bows on the market today. This year, Bear Archery is bringing back the "Throwback" Legit as an exclusively model available only at Bear Authorized Dealers. The nostalgic throwback finish features Fred Bear Camo limbs with either an olive green or shadow black riser. The bow offers the same remarkable adjustability from a 14” to 30” draw length and from 10 to 70 lbs. draw weight. All adjustments can be made without the need for a bow press. The bow comes ready to hunt equipped with Trophy Ridge accessories – 4-pin sight, 5-Spot quiver, 6" stabilizer, V-Biscuit, No-tie peep sight & D loop. The Legit weighs an incredible 3.6 lbs. and blasts arrows down range at 315 feet per second. The Legit's dual cam system provides a class leading smooth draw cycle.

description:
EASTON GHOST DOUBLE BARREL (-11) FASTPITCH SOFTBALL BAT

IT’S TIME TO MAKE SOME NOISE! The hottest bat in the game is back, now with Sonic Comp Technology. Featuring patented Double Barrel construction, providing the best pop, feel and sound with a massive sweet spot. The Ghost Double Barrel is built with Sonic Comp, a higher-performing and more durable composite material with the iconic Ghost sound heard on all fields. Sonic Comp is specifically engineered with the lowest barrel compression and improved durability for maximum performance. ConneXionTM Technology optimizes a more ‘stiff’ barrel flex and maximizes energy transfer while eliminating vibration, resulting in an all-around solid feel at contact. name: SRAM X01 Eagle 12-Speed Chain
description:
SRAM X01 EAGLE 12-SPEED CHAIN

It might look normal from the outside, but the engineering inside this incredible chain design makes possible a gear range previously found only in 2-chainring drivetrains. And it's also the biggest contributor to the Eagle drivetrain's ultra-smooth, precise, durable and quiet performance. The Eagle chain's links have a smooth radius, with no sharp edges or chamfers, which yield a significant reduction in noise, friction and wear on chainrings and cassette cogs. This design also allows for a flatter plate, which means more consistent chain riveting and greater overall strength. HARD CHROME technology extends the chain's optimal performance life, with 4x the wear resistance of other chains.

FEATURES

Groundbreaking chain design and technology
Eagle PowerLock chain connector with FLOW LINK technology provides better chain-guiding and increased longevity
Quietest, strongest and most wear-resistant chain in the world
Improved wear resistance on Eagle cassettes and rings

TECH SPECS

COMPAT - SPEED (CN) 12s-Eagle
OUTER LINK FINISH: Nickel
COLOR - OUTER LINK: Silver
INNER LINK FINISH: Chrome Plated
COLOR - INNER LINK: Silver
CHAIN CONNECTOR: PowerLock
CHAIN LENGTH (LINKS): 126 links
PIN VARIANT: Hollow Pin
WEIGHT: 239 g (based on 114 links)

name: Fenwick Aetos Fly Rod
description:
FENWICK AETOS FLY ROD

Fenwick's Aetos Fly Rod is an entry-level rod geared towards the anglers among us who want a forgiving, user-friendly, and versatile performance. Its affordable price tag and solid componentry give us everything we need to perfect our casting technique, pin down our roll cast, and wrangle that first fish we hook into. Its graphite blank provides a fast action feel, while the AAA grade cork handle offers up a highly intuitive casting motion.

FEATURES

Beginner-friendly fly rod with Fenwick's lowest price tag
Graphite blank is lighter and stronger than carbon fiber
AAA-grade cork grips provide optimal control
Fast action increases line speed with plenty of reserve power
Anodized aluminum reel seat is extremely durable and lightweight
Included cloth-covered tube protects rod during travel and storage

TECH SPECS

Material: Nano Composite Technology (graphite)
Length: 6ft, 6ft 6in, 7ft, 8ft, 8ft 6in, 9ft, 10ft, 11ft 1in
Action: fast
Rod Weight: 3wt, 4wt, 5wt, 6wt, 7wt, 8wt, 6/7wt, 7/8wt, 8/9wt
Handle: reverse half-wells cork
Reel Seats: anodized aluminum
Pieces: 4
Claimed Weight: [3wt 6ft] 2.4oz, [4wt 6ft 6in] 2.5oz, [3wt 7ft] 2.5oz, [4wt 7ft] 2.9oz
Recommended Use: river fishing, stillwater fishing

name: Salomon Speedcross 6 Gore-Tex Shoe - Men's
description:
SALOMON SPEEDCROSS 6 GORE-TEX SHOE - MEN'S

SPEEDCROSS 6 GORE-TEX needs no introductions. True to its legendary roots and trail icon status, this version is lighter with an even more powerful, grippy connection to the ground and faster mud evacuation. Featuring a waterproof and breathable Gore-Tex membrane ideal for wet and muddy conditions, a revamped upper and classic SPEEDCROSS comfort.

FEATURES

Mud Contagrip
Built for maximum grip on loose, soft, rugged, and uneven surfaces, Mud Contagrip uses deep, sharp lugs made from a compound that focuses on adhesion.
EnergyCell+ is a high-rebound midsole compound that provides exceptional energy return along with substantial cushioning and durability.
GORE-TEX keeps your feet dry -from the outside as well as from the inside.
Anti-debris Mesh
Tight mesh that prevents debris from being trapped between your foot and the footbed.
Ripstop fabric
Woven fabrics, often made of nylon, with reinforcement to resist tearing, ripping and abrasion.
Quicklace
Minimalistic and strong lace for one-pull tightening. Easy-on, easy-off.
Recycled material
Materials made from recycled products such as PET bottles or material waste

name: Vans Slip-On TRK Shoe
description:
VANS SLIP-ON TRK SHOE

Sandals aren't for everyone, but wearing shoes to the beach isn't always ideal, either—and that's why Vans welcomed the Slip-On TRK to the Vans family. Just go surf, rinse, then repeat. Taking the Classic Slip-On silhouette to a whole new level, the Slip-On TRK combines all the Vans DNA that you know and love with a durable, single piece injected construction, deconstructed checkerboard drainage holes for breathability, and an oversized reverse waffle sole. Designed to be lightweight and fully rinseable, the Slip-On TRK is easy to pack for your next adventure, so you can slip-on and on and on...

FEATURES

BREATHABLE AND RINSEABLE: Drainage holes mean that whatever goes in goes right back out.
A ONE-PIECE, SOLID, DURABLE DESIGN: A single-piece injected construction makes the Trek Slip-On collapsible and packable, as well as durable.

name: Groove Life Belt - Men's
description:
GROOVE LIFE BELT - MEN'S

The Groove Belt is good for the office, the woods, the backyard, and everything in between! Just adjust to fit once and forget. The Groove Belt has the perfect amount of stretch giving you the most comfortable all-day fit ever. The buckle uses high-strength, neodymium magnets for an easy, seamless snap-on/snap-off. And includes what Groove likes to call Stiff-Tech (aka no folding in your belt loops).

FEATURES

Between our proprietary webbing, rare earth neodymium magnets and A380 aluminum alloy buckle.
We designed the end to neatly tuck behind the belt. For the occasional rogue fly away, we’ve added our secure keeper loop.
The correct term is neodymium magnets but we like to say Strong as Hell. Just listen to that SNAP.

name: Browning Hell's Canyon Speed Javelin-FM Vest - Men's

breadcrumbs.name: Browning Hell's Canyon Speed Javelin-FM Vest - Men's

description:
BROWNING HELL'S CANYON SPEED JAVELIN-FM VEST - MEN'S

Rugged and lightweight hunting vest. High mobility design and function.

Keep moving... fast. The Javelin-FM vest is designed for mobility above all else. Rugged enough to keep from tearing in thick brush and protect your body from abrasion: Light enough that you'll barely realize that you are wearing it. Trudge through the mud in it or get it bloody while you gut a deer - rinse it off quickly in a stream, shake it off, and you're good to go.

FM = Fast and Mobile. Browning Hell's Canyon Speed clothing won't slow you down or restrict your movement. Fully articulated, lightweight, and packable - Speed clothing will keep you comfortable but the highest design priority was to not slow down the athlete hunter who uses it.

FEATURES

Rugged, lightweight double weave soft shell fabric
Water/wind resistant and extremely breathable
Zip-through collar
Lower zippered hand pockets
Two Napoleon chest pockets
Water-resistant front zipper with internal storm flap and chin guard
Internal pockets for smaller gear

name: GU Roctane Energy Gel
description:
GU ROCTANE ENERGY GEL

Whether it's half way through your work day and you're slowing down or you need a pick me up before your workout, the GU Roctane Energy Gel has got you covered. If you demand the most from your energy sources, Roctane Energy Gel delivers on that demand with amino acids that reduce mental fatigue and decrease muscle damage that will help you keep going throughout the day. A step up from GU's original Energy Gel, Roctane has more sodium and electrolytes for increased hydration. To wrap it all up, 35mg of caffeine gives you an extra boost for your workouts.

FEATURES

24 individual gels
More sodium and amino acids than original GU Energy Gel
Fructose provides a fast-acting dose of energy
Maltodextrin is absorbed slowly and sent to your muscles
Vital electrolytes stabilize your blood chemistry and hydration levels
Caffeine adds an extra kick to your power
Sea salt supplies a host of minerals
Gluten-free, vegan, and KORC certified

Designed to add a contemporary finish to any style, The Roger Advantage is the third tennis-inspired sneaker to join the collection co-created with Roger Federer. name: Babolat Propulse All Court Junior Tennis Shoe - Youth

breadcrumbs.name: Babolat Propulse All Court Junior Tennis Shoe - Youth

description:
BABOLAT PROPULSE ALL COURT JUNIOR TENNIS SHOE - YOUTH

The Propulse Junior is designed for young players who already work their shoes hard. Inspired by the adult model, it provides an excellent balance of support, durability and comfort thanks to the strap in the midfoot, the protective piece in the forefoot and the Michelin sole designed to last on all court surfaces.

FEATURES

SUPPORT

The Propulse Jr is the ideal shoe for young competitors who want to develop their game. The Power Belt is like a "seat belt" that keeps the foot secure even through the most demanding shots.

COMFORT AND SUPPORT

Because theyrealways thinking about comfort, they've given the Propulse Jr an EVA midsole and the Kompressor system to protect the ankle from sudden impact throughout training and matches.

SOLE DURABILITY

They've worked with Michelin to create a sole made of a special kind of rubber for each court surface.

TECH SPECS

POWER BELT

The Powerbelt is a wide strap that wraps around the midfoot and offers both exceptional lateral support and an almost tailored fit all around the foot.

ORTHOLITE DIE CUT

The properties of the foam composition mean that the OrthoLite die cut insole provides exceptional comfort, breathability and durability.

KOMPRESSOR

TPR (Thermo Plastic Rubber) tube compression system positioned beneath the heel for exceptional shock absorption.

MICHELIN TENNIS

The Michelin Original rubber composition has proven its worth over the past 15 years and beyond, It offers a great combination of grip and durability to meet the extreme demands of tennis footwork.

Steeped in the alpine, this versatile hoodie has warmed climbers, hikers, backcountry skiers and downtown commuters. Coreloft Compact insulation retains warmth even if wet and has loft retention that withstands years of packing and unpacking. name: The North Face Jester Backpack
description:
THE NORTH FACE JESTER BACKPACK

TNF's classic Jester pack has a padded laptop sleeve, simplified organization, and it can stand up completely unsupported. It’s also endorsed by the American Chiropractic Association.

FEATURES

TNF's FlexVent suspension system, certified by the American Chiropractic Association, features a flexible yoke built from custom injection-molded shoulder straps; an unbelievably comfortable, padded back panel; and a highly breathable lumbar panel
Two webbing top handles make it convenient to open and provide a balanced carry so it doesn’t swing into your side when you’re walking
Pack stands on its own for easy loading and unloading
Padded 15'' laptop sleeve helps protect laptop from bumps and falls
Huge main compartment holds books and binders for a day on campus
Front compartment simplifies organization for the modern user while maintaining essential features for storage such as secure-zip pockets, a tablet sleeve and a key clip
Two external water bottle pockets
Stylish front bungee system for additional storage
360-degree reflectivity
Sternum strap

name: Asics Gel-Game 9 Tennis Shoe - Women's
description:
ASICS GEL-GAME 9 TENNIS SHOE - WOMEN'S

Both durable and comfortable, the GEL-GAME 9 tennis shoe is versatile for the recreational athlete who’s playing several times per week. Preserving its excellent support properties, Asic's focus this season was to improve the shoe's ventilation and flexibility. Featuring an open mesh design on the upper to improve airflow and keep feet cool, this shoe is complemented with synthetic leather overlays and a PU (polyurethane) film that offers improved stability when making abrupt transitions. The TRUSSTIC technology in the midsole generates better stability on the court. At the same time, the new tooling combines an EVA midsole foam with GEL technology cushioning in the forefoot to increase shock absorption. Additionally, the improved outsole offers better flexibility and a more durable design.

FEATURES

PU and mesh design improves breathability
TRUSSTIC technology improves stability
GEL technology cushioning provides excellent shock absorption

name: NEMO Moonlite Reclining Chair
description:
NEMO MOONLITE RECLINING CHAIR

One Giant Leap In Ultralight Seating

Take Moonlite into the backcountry and experience the feeling of weightlessness as you lean back under the stars. Easy to set up and barely noticeable in your pack, Moonlite is your go-to chair for every adventure from a picnic in the park to an extended backpacking adventure. Oversized tubes, paired with forged aluminum hubs, create exceptional strength and stability. And best of all, Moonlite is the only chair of its kind with an adjustable seating position, making it ideal for dining or reclining. The exceptional comfort of the Moonlite™ chair comes from a custom engineered, asymmetrical mesh that stretches to accommodate and support a variety of body types without needing seams. This unique seamless seat attaches to the frame with y molded, ball-and-socket connectors that rotate and align with your body to avoid uncomfortable pressure points. The adjustable seating position, oversized tubes, aluminum hubs and seamless seat combine to make a unique and transformative sitting experience in a packed weight and size that can come along for any adventure. True to our mission of sustainability, Moonlite uses 100% post-consumer recycled materials for the webbing and bluesign approved mesh seat.

FEATURES

The seamless seat design is made possible by custom engineered asymmetric mesh that conforms better to different body shapes.
Intuitive design, with shock corded frame components and satisfying ball-and-socket seat attachments.
High quality, precision hardware builds confidence and looks sharp.
Premium forged 6061 series aluminum hubs and oversized 7001 series aluminum tubes are built for a lifetime of stability and reliability.
Each pole in the frame has a unique diameter and shape optimized for weight and strength.
Patent-pending reclining system allows you to adjust your sitting angle for dining, working on a laptop, or carefree relaxing.
100% Post-consumer recycled materials are used in asymmetrical mesh, edge binding, and webbing — asymmetrical mesh and reclining hardware are bluesign® approved.
Includes a carrying case.
Protected by the NEMO Lifetime Warranty.

TECH SPECS

Packed Weight: 1 lb , 14 oz / 850 g
Packed Size: 4.0 x 4.0 x 14.0 in / 10 x 10 x 35 cm
Dimensions: 20 x 20 x 26 in / 52 x 51 x 65 cm
Capacity: 300 lbs / 136 kgs
Stuff Sack: Zippered storage bag
Frame: Aluminum
Fabric: Polyester

name: Big Agnes Rapide SL Insulated Sleeping Pad

breadcrumbs.name: Big Agnes Rapide SL Insulated Sleeping Pad

description:
BIG AGNES RAPIDE SL INSULATED SLEEPING PAD

When it comes to superlight, three-season comfort, the Rapide SL Insulated pad stands alone. Built with offset I-Beam construction, this proprietary design reduces weight while providing multi-directional support for consistent stability and comfort. This superlight air chamber pad sleeps warmer using PrimaLoft Silver Insulation and is third party rated with an R-Value of 4.2 for use through three-seasons. The Rapide SL Insulated is lighter, tougher, more packable, easy to inflate/deflate, and provides superior performance and packability for any adventure. Save your breath for the miles ahead and use the included pad inflation sack to inflate.

FEATURES

R-Value: 4.2, Three-Season
3.5” / 9cm thick pad with 4.25” / 11cm larger outer chambers keep you comfortably cradled in the middle of the pad
Quilted top provides a cushioned pillowy sleeping surface
Durable, superlight nylon double ripstop
PrimaLoft Silver Insulation working with a heat reflective barrier traps body heat and reflects it back, so you stay comfortable as the temperatures drop
Proprietary offset I-Beam construction reduces weight and provides consistent stability and comfort
Aviation-grade TPU lamination provides ultimate weld strength and dependability
Quieter materials than other pads on the market
Antimicrobial treatment inside the pad prevents microorganism growth
Individually inflated and tested at our factory ensuring 100% quality performance
High-volume valve allows for efficient and easy inflation, super-fast deflation, and micro adjustments
Includes pad inflation sack, protective storage sack, replacement valve seal, and 3M repair patches

TECH SPECS

Durable, superlight nylon double rip-stop fabric
Aviation-grade TPU lamination technology provides ultimate weld strength and durability
Quieter materials than other pads on the market
PrimaLoft Silver Insulation
Layer of heat reflective film
High-volume valve allows for efficient and easy inflation, super-fast deflation and micro adjustments
Valve illustration copy: One-way inflation valve with micro air-pressure adjust button
Quick-deflation valve

DJINN carabiners have a wide rope contact zone to limit rope drag and provide greater durability for both carabiner and rope. The design of the bent gate allows the rope to be clipped efficiently. name: On Cloudrunner Running Shoe - Women's
description:
ON CLOUDRUNNER RUNNING SHOE - WOMEN'S

As runners, getting out there can be hard. The Cloudrunner is made soft. Yet also supportive. With instant comfort so awesome that just stepping in makes you want to head out, and a light, cushioned ride that encourages you to keep running. What's better than foam underfoot? Foam right around your foot. The cradle and cushioning of the bottom unit are enhanced by the foam around the collar in the soft-touch tongue. In fact, every element is Swiss-engineered to remove discomfort as a reason not to run. With the Cloudrunner, there's no stopping you.

FEATURES

Engineered mesh upper made for supportive comfort that also lets your feet breathe
Soft to the touch and ventilating, this is comfort made for the long run
Wider Speedboard and a cradle-shaped construction support you at (literally) every step of your running journey
Takes the impact out of asphalt with CloudTec® cushioning in ultralight Zero-Gravity foam
Absorbs both vertical and horizontal forces every strike, the streets never felt so soft
Outsole has rubber grip pattern for traction on the road

TECH SPECS

Over 90% of the polyester content, and over 30% of the entire shoe, is from recycled materials
Weight: 8.8 oz / 250 g

description:
STANLEY THE ICEFLOW FLIP STRAW TUMBLER - 30OZ

This bold, colorful tumbler is made to keep you hydrated in a fully functional style. Ideal for car commutes or workouts at home, it has a built-in flip straw for easy and effortless sipping. Snap it shut and the double-wall vacuum insulation will keep your drink fully leakproof and extra cold for hours. It fits comfortably in your vehicle’s cup holder (treadmills and spin cycles, too!), and the folding handle lets you quickly grab and go.

To help you live a sustainable lifestyle, the IceFlow Tumbler is made in part from recycled plastics sourced from discarded fishing nets, sparing water of plastic waste.

name: Petzl GriGri Belay Device
description:
ASSISTED BRAKING FOR MORE COMFORT - THE PETZL GRIGRI BELAY DEVICE.

This belay device will make your belaying easier and more comfortable. The Petzl GriGri Belay Device features assisted breaking which activates when a climber falls. You can lower a climber with smooth control thanks to the ergonomic handle and progressive cam action.

FEATURES

Designed for experienced belayers, the assisted braking function activates when a climber falls; the device pivots, the rope tightens and the cam pinches to block the rope
Always catch falls and feed slack using standard belay techniques, keeping a hand on the brake side of the rope to help engage the cam
Balanced design is optimized for 8.9-10.5 mm rope diameters and is simple to use for belaying both lead or top-rope climbers
Rope installation diagram is engraved on both the interior and exterior of the device
Camming mechanism enables exceptional descent control when lowering
Ergonomic handle and progressive cam action allow you to easily lower a climber with smooth descent control
Durably constructed with aluminum side plates, stainless-steel cam and friction plate and a reinforced nylon handle
Certified to CE EN 15151-1 and UIAA standards

TECH SPECS

Weight: 175 grams

Fits Rope Sizes 8.5-11mm, single

name: Asics Gel-challenger 13 Tennis Shoe - Women's
description:
ASICS GEL-CHALLENGER 13 TENNIS SHOE - WOMEN'S

The Gel-Challenger 13 Tennis Shoe creates the stability you need when you're covering the baseline, so you can keep your mind focused on controlling the point. The shoe's supportive upper keeps your feet locked-in on the shoe's platform. It creates a reinforced feel during volleys or when you're dropping back to track down deep lob shots. WINGWALL technology is placed in the sidewall to improve stability during side-to-side movements. This feature offers good support, so you can step into your shot and stroke the ball with more pace.

FEATURES

PGuard Toe Protector
WINGWALL technology improves stability
AHAR Plus outsole
Ortholite Sockliner
Rearfoot and forefoot GEL Technology cushioning system

name: Asics Gel-Kayano 29 Running Shoe - Men's
description:
ASICS GEL-KAYANO 29 RUNNING SHOE - MEN'S

The GEL-KAYANO 29 shoe creates a stable running experience and a more responsive feel underfoot. Featuring a low-profile external heel counter, this piece comfortably cradles your foot with advanced rearfoot support. Asics also updated the midsole with FF BLAST PLUS cushioning. This helps keep the shoe lightweight while creating a more energized rebound in each step. A LITETRUSS stability feature is placed on the midsole’s inside angle. It’s designed to help keep your foot from rolling too far inward during your stride.

FEATURES

Engineered knit upper: Improves breathability.
Redesigned external heel counter: Helps keep the foot stable and provide a more comfortable stride.
LITETRUSS technology: Improves medial support and midfoot integrity.
3D SPACE CONSTRUCTION feature: Improves compression at footstrike.
Rearfoot GEL technology cushioning: Provides good shock absorption.
FF BLAST PLUS cushioning: Provides lightweight impact absorption and a responsive rebound.
OrthoLite X-55 sockliner: Improves comfort.
Reflective details: Improve visibility.
AHARPLUS heel plug: Improves the outsole durability.

TECH SPECS

At least 50% of the shoe’s main upper material is made with recycled materials to reduce waste and carbon emissions
The sockliner is produced with the solution dyeing process that reduces water usage by approximately 33% and carbon emissions by approximately 45% compared to the conventional dyeing technology

name: Vans Authentic Shoe
description:
VANS AUTHENTIC SHOE

Born in Anaheim, California in 1966, the Authentic is the original Vans heritage style. Originally know as Vans #44 Deck Shoes, the Authentic became an immediate cult icon, and has embodied Van's “Off The Wall” attitude ever since. Constructed with a simple low top, lace-up profile, this classic shoe also features sturdy canvas uppers, metal eyelets, and signature rubber waffle outsoles.

breadcrumbs.name: Patagonia Capilene Cool Daily Short Sleeve Shirt - Men's

description:
PATAGONIA CAPILENE COOL DAILY SHORT SLEEVE SHIRT - MEN'S

The perfect shirt for just about any occasion when the mercury starts to rise, Patagonia's Capilene Cool Daily Short-Sleeve Shirt delivers cooling comfort and moisture-wicking performance for everything from long day hikes to casual strolls on the boardwalk. The new Capilene Cool technology takes Patagonia's trusted baselayer fabric and engineers it more specifically for hot weather, keeping you dryer and cooler when the heat is unbeatable. It's even got Polygiene anti-odor technology to fight the funk when you decide to hit the town after leaving the trail. Add on a stretchy construction for easier climbing, a special softness-enhancing treatment, and a clean everyday look, and this shirt is bound to be a staple of your summer wardrobe no matter the day's adventure.

Lightweight shirt for casual and active pursuits in the summer

Minimal seaming reduces chafing on long trail runs

The OluKai Men's Hokua Sandal is a leather thong sandal for walking the sandy beaches day in and day out. Built to be durable for the rigors of ocean-side living, the synthetic leather strap is water-resistant and stitched with heavyweight deco. name: Gerber Armbar Slim Drive Multi Tool

breadcrumbs.name: Gerber Armbar Slim Drive Multi Tool

description:
GERBER ARMBAR SLIM DRIVE MULTI TOOL

The Armbar Slim Drive takes a minimalist approach while giving you the tools to help you with what you do the most: cutting, driving, and opening a beer. What more could you need in an ultra thin profile? A 2-1/2” long driver with two-sided 1/4” bit has the reach to tighten that fastener without busting your knuckles. Not to mention the easy one-hand access to the 2-1/2” frame lock blade that can rip through anything you put in front of it. Don’t get caught unprepared, support your daily carry with this robust tool in your pocket or on your key chain to get out of any jam.

FEATURES

2” extension bit driver to get to those hard to reach spots.
Full 2.5” plain edge blade that can be accessed with one hand.
Large tool tabs and access points for fumble free operation with only your thumb.
When the work is done, you’re ready with a bottle opener close at hand.

TECH SPECS

Frame lock
Blade length: 2.5”
Width: 0.6”
Closed length: 3.8”
Open length: 6.75”

description:
HOKA CLIFTON 9 SHOE - MEN'S

Presenting the ninth edition of the prestigious Hoka Clifton series, lighter and more cushioned than all its previous versions. Not just diminishing weight, but also adding an extra 3mm in stack height, the Clifton 9 introduces an invigorated underfoot sensation with a nimble new foam and an enhanced outsole pattern. Tongue featuring a gusset design

Designed with inherently stable geometry

name: Vans Era Shoe
description:
VANS ERA SHOE

The Vans Era, originally called the Vans #95, was brought to life in 1976 and made popular by the legendary Z-Boys of Santa Monica. It was the first shoe to include Vans' famous padded collar, completely changing the game for comfort, and it remains a favorite for creative people worldwide. Featuring sturdy canvas uppers in a range of heritage colorways, the Era energizes their timeless low top silhouette with effortless style. In addition to the supportive collar, this classic lace-up shoe comes equipped with metal eyelets and signature rubber waffle outsoles.

name: Lux Pro Waterproof Ultralight Led Rechargeable Headlamp

breadcrumbs.name: Lux Pro Waterproof Ultralight Led Rechargeable Headlamp

description:
LUX PRO WATERPROOF ULTRALIGHT LED RECHARGEABLE HEADLAMP

The LUXPRO CUBI738 is an ultra-compact rechargeable and waterproof LED headlamp. This headlamp is bright with over 360 lumens. It's versatile with 7 modes: high+, high, medium, flood white, flood green, flood red, and hidden strobe. A dual button allows you to easily cycle through the 7 modes. Designed with the 45-degree adjustable headlamp base to shine the light exactly where it's needed. A blue LED battery life indicator, located on the side of the headlamp, makes it easy to know when the battery needs to be charged. It comes with a micro-USB cable to charge and fully recharges in approximately 1 hour. The headband is comfortable and adjustable for a stable fit. This headlamp is lightweight and micro-sized making it ideal for runners, backpackers, campers, and more. This light is completely waterproof with an IPX7 rating. Meaning it can be submerged in 3 feet of water for up to 30 minutes.

FEATURES

3.5h max runtime
Rechargeable and Waterproof
7 modes including high plus
White, red and green floodlight options
Adjustable headband
IPX7 waterproof rating

TECH SPECS

Beam Distance: 14m - 183m
Battery Count/Size: Li-poly; 3.7V 250mAh

These shears also include a tension control knob, so you can adjust the blades for cutting especially dense branches and stems. Fully hardened, precision-ground steel blades stay sharp, and a low-friction, rust-resistant coating makes every cut easier. name: Skratch Labs Sport Hydration Mix
description:
SKRATCH LABS SPORT HYDRATION MIX

Skratch's Sport Hydration Drink Mix was created for a simple purpose - to replace the electrolytes lost in sweat and to provide a little bit of energy when working out, without offending your palate or gut.

Skratch initially created this drink because some of the world’s best athletes needed better. Conventional sports drinks made them sick. They were undrinkable - too sweet, over-flavored, and didn’t even replace what was lost in sweat – which defeated the whole purpose, like fighting thirst with more thirst.

The best athletes needed something to safely hydrate, something to quench their thirst, and something to help them perform better. So with their help, Skratch reimagined sports drinks, stripping down what used to be a neon-colored carnival to its bare essentials. In the process, they learned that simple wasn’t just better for elite athletes - it was better for everyone who works hard and sweats.

The result is a sports drink with minimal sugar (4g per 100 ml) and a ratio of sugar (glucose + fructose) that is optimized for faster absorption, an electrolyte profile that actually matches what is lost in sweat (800 mg sodium, 80 mg potassium, 100 mg calcium, and 80 mg of magnesium per liter), and only real fruit for flavor for a light and refreshing taste that you can drink all day. That’s it - less sugar, the right electrolyte profile, and real fruit. So, if you’ve never met a sports drink you wanted to take home, your luck is about to change.

FEATURES

50% less sugar and nearly 2x the sodium of the leading sports drink*
Verified non-GMO, gluten-free, dairy-free and vegan
Made with real fruit

name: Pflueger Supreme XT Spinning Reel
description:
PFLUEGER SUPREME XT SPINNING REEL

The Pflueger Supreme XT Spinning Reel is renowned for its super lightweight magnesium body and rotor and an exceptionally smooth retrieve. Even after several seasons of hard use, don't be surprised if the Supreme XT is as smooth as the day it came out of the box. Plus, the gear ratio lets you haul in line quickly and is necessary when a fish runs at you. Just as smooth as the effortless retrieve, the sealed carbon drag is easy to set and strong when cranked down to combat larger fish. Corrosion-resistant, you can use these reels for everything from freshwater to surf fishing. The aluminum spool is braid-ready and comes with a lightweight carbon fiber handle and EVA knob. Light, strong, and reliable, try one and you may soon want the whole series of Pflueger Supreme XT Spinning Reels!

FEATURES

Magnesium Body and Rotor
Braid Ready Spool
Sealed Carbon Drag

name: Sram Gx Eagle 12 Sp Rear Derailleur - Max 52t Lunar | Rear Derailleur

breadcrumbs.name: Sram Gx Eagle 12 Sp Rear Derailleur - Max 52t Lunar | Rear Derailleur

description:
SRAM GX EAGLE 12 SP REAR DERAILLEUR - MAX 52T LUNAR | REAR DERAILLEUR

SRAM Eagle just got a little better now with extended range! If Eagle just isn't enough for you they've now added 2 teeth to the cassette! If you need a little extra help on the climbs but don't want to sacrifice your top speed by dropping the front ring this is just what you need! Upgrading or setting up a 10-52 Eagle drivetrain? You will need a new derailleur since the added range is just a little too much for the 10-52 derailluers. That means if you are getting the new cassette you will want one of these. If you've still got some life left in your drivetrain, don't worry, that Eagle shifter and chain you have is still good to use for the extended range!

FEATURES

Will not work with front derailleur drive trains
Mounting system and re-positioned Cage Lock offer greater durability
Sealed cartridge pulley bearings

name: On Cloudflow Running Shoe - Men's
description:
ON CLOUDFLOW RUNNING SHOE - MEN'S

The ON Running Cloudflow is a lightweight but very well cushioned power running shoe and offers you a particularly comfortable and reactive running experience based on the characteristic CloudTec outsole. The road specialist has been specifically improved compared to its predecessor and is an excellent partner for training and competitions. For all distances up to the supreme discipline of the marathon, it provides a great, extremely fluid running feeling and supports you optimally on your way to new best times.

The runner achieves an optimal absorption of impact energy and a flowing conversion into a powerful, explosive push-off through the targeted coordination of its 18 Cloud elements made of the new Helion foam with a pre-tensioned stabiliser plate, the model-specific "Cloudflow Speedboard".

Consistency is expressed in the Cloudflow through the successful symbiosis of sole technology with a comfortable, sock-like fit. The adaptable, lightweight, and breathable upper material fits the shape of the foot without gaps and offers improved support, especially in the midfoot area, thanks to the optimised power transmission of the lacing.

FEATURES

Design offers increased speed and comfort.
Ultra light super foam.
Technical mesh offers a secure fit.
Steps with more power.

Enjoy cocoa, coffee or a gourmet freeze-dried meal in a jiffy with the new Jetboil Flash cooking system, which boils water in 100 seconds, allowing you to conserve fuel and dig in faster.
