name: Vans Gum Style 36 Shoe - Men's
description:
VANS GUM STYLE 36 SHOE - MEN'S

Tapping into Van's history, Style 36 was Vans’ first Sidestripe shoe brought to life in 1977. Though the Vans Sidestripe has since become the unmistakable—and instantly recognizable—hallmark of the Vans brand, back then it was just a random doodle drawn by founder Paul Van Doren. It even had a different name: the “jazz stripe.” Honoring the style that launched an icon, the Style 36 is made with classic canvas and suede uppers in a range of colorways. This low top, lace-up shoe also features vintage styling, reinforced toe caps, supportive padded collars, and signature rubber waffle outsoles. Vans’ original low top, Sidestripe shoe Classic suede and canvas uppers Lace-up closure Vintage styling Reinforced toe caps Supportive padded collars Signature rubber waffle outsoles

name: Salomon X Ultra 4 Mid Gore-Tex Hiking Boot - Men's

breadcrumbs.name: Salomon X Ultra 4 Mid Gore-Tex Hiking Boot - Men's

description:
SALOMON X ULTRA 4 MID GORE-TEX HIKING BOOT - MEN'S

Get ready to power through uphills and descents with this wide-fit and mid-cut GORE-TEX version of the X-ULTRA 4. It is as agile as a trail-running shoe but with all the stability, grip and waterproof protection you need to tackle technical terrain. Equipped with a new chassis, the shoe is even better at protecting sensitive articulations without compromising freedom of movement.

To help reduce impact on the environment, no harmful PFCs are used to ensure the water repellency of Salomon shoes. Waterproof GORE-TEX models are free from PFCec .

FEATURES

Outsole

All Terrain Contagrip delivers durability & confidence on wet, dry, hard or loose surfaces.
Chevron lug design with deep penetration and multi-directional grip, will improve your traction on soft surfaces like mud or loose dirt.
Advanced Chassis is a molded insert embedded in the outsole. Providing strong lateral support and reassuring protection, it also delivers optimal mobility and flexibility.

Upper

Water-repellent treatment is applied to provide extra protection, ensuring that the fabric does not absorb water during light rain and showers.
SensiFit cradles the foot from the midsole to the lacing system, providing a secure, snug, and virtually customized fit all around the foot.
Active Support mobile wings help hold the foot in place and accompany its movement, adapting to its shape and volume.
Traditional lacing system
Gusseted tongue
Protective toe cap and mudguard

Liner

Soft, breathable textile lining for extreme comfort
Molded to match the contours of your foot, the OrthoLite insole provides superior cushioning, breathability and durability.
GORE-TEX membrane
EnergyCell EVA foam for shock attenuation

TECH SPECS

Drop: 11 mm
Heel stack height: 31.5 mm
Forefoot stack height: 20.5 mm
Weight: 420 g

name: Asics Gel-Rocket 10 Shoe - Women's
description:
ASICS GEL-ROCKET 10 SHOE - WOMEN'S

A multi-purpose indoor court shoe, the GEL-ROCKET 10 offering continues to deliver excellent cushioning for a range of court athletes. This shoe is designed with a flexible upper construction that can help feet bend more naturally and assist players in moving more freely. Additionally, this shoe also features synthetic leather overlays that improve support in the forefoot and help athletes make confident cuts. Designed with a TRUSSTIC application in the midsole, this application improves stability during quick transitions. Creating excellent comfort, the GEL technology cushioning unit in the heel is functional for providing better shock absorption. A wrap-up outsole and outrigger is a functional support component during side-to-side movements. In contrast, the heel wrap-up expands the contact area during the landing phase of your stride to help generate a smoother landing. Lastly, the flexible grooves in the outsole are complemented with a side grip design that improves flexibility on the court.

breadcrumbs.name: CamelBak Chute Mag 32oz Bottle w/ Tritan Renew

description:
CAMELBAK CHUTE MAG 32OZ BOTTLE W/ TRITAN RENEW

Your daily hydration habit with a sustainable twist. The lightweight and durable Chute Mag water bottle is now made with Tritan Renew, a highly durable and lightweight plastic made with 50% recycled material. Besides the do-good construction, you’ll love the high flow universal magnetic cap. It's leak-proof when closed, stows securely out of the way when drinking, and is compatible with Eddy+ and Carry Cap vessels. The comfortable carry handle makes for grab-and-go convenience and when the day is over, just toss in the dishwasher and prepare for your next adventure. Tritan Renew is made using Polyester Renewal Technology, a recycling process that’s more efficient than standard mechanical recycling, producing new material with less demand on finite resources. Odor and stain resistant, and free of BPA, BPS, and BPF.

Magnetic cap stows out of the way when drinking

name: Scott Aspect eRIDE 920 Off-Road eBike - 2022
description:
SCOTT ASPECT ERIDE 920 OFF-ROAD EBIKE - 2022

The SCOTT Aspect eRIDE 920 features proven electric assist technology in a comfortable off-road package. With an integrated battery, and powered by a 625wh Bosch drive system, the Aspect eRIDE will give you hours of trail riding energy. Rack and fender available.

Light Ready
In order to mount a front or rear light, they have already routed the cables in the frame, and there is no need for an extra battery – the power comes straight from the drive unit battery. (Light not included)

eRide Advanced Design
With this new E-Bike generation, the design has been pushed further than ever before. More than a battery integrated into the frame, Scott see's the bike as a system where every part must be taken into consideration. Therefore, to improve the integration, they have worked a lot on the line continuity but also on the design balance from the headtube to the dropouts. Enjoy a bike with a unique character!

Bosch Power Tube
Thanks to their range, long service life, intelligent battery management system and easy handling, Bosch Power Tube lithium-ion batteries are among the most modern on the market. All those decades of Bosch experience has paid off!

Rack & Fenders
Feel free to install a rack and the corresponding fender set. The frame has dedicated fixation points for a clean and reliable solution. (Not included)

Bosch Performance CX Gen 4 Drive Unit
The new Performance CX generation is now 48% smaller and 25% lighter compare to the previous generation. More compact but no less powerful, the new Bosch Performance CX Generation 4 comes with a maximum power output of 75Nm and 340%. Choose between 5 assist modes or opt for the comfort of the eMTB mode which automatically adapts the assistance like an automatic gearbox does in a car.

***Please note that bike specifications are subject to change without prior notice***

Features

Frame:

Alloy frame

descriptionHtml:
SCOTT ASPECT ERIDE 920 OFF-ROAD EBIKE - 2022

The SCOTT Aspect eRIDE 920 features proven electric assist technology in a comfortable off-road package. With an integrated battery, and powered by a 625wh Bosch drive system, the Aspect eRIDE will give you hours of trail riding energy. Rack and fender available.

Light Ready
In order to mount a front or rear light, they have already routed the cables in the frame, and there is no need for an extra battery – the power comes straight from the drive unit battery. (Light not included)

eRide Advanced Design
With this new E-Bike generation, the design has been pushed further than ever before. More than a battery integrated into the frame, Scott see's the bike as a system where every part must be taken into consideration. Therefore, to improve the integration, they have worked a lot on the line continuity but also on the design balance from the headtube to the dropouts. Enjoy a bike with a unique character!

Bosch Power Tube
Thanks to their range, long service life, intelligent battery management system and easy handling, Bosch Power Tube lithium-ion batteries are among the most modern on the market. All those decades of Bosch experience has paid off!

Rack & Fenders
Feel free to install a rack and the corresponding fender set. The frame has dedicated fixation points for a clean and reliable solution. (Not included)

Bosch Performance CX Gen 4 Drive Unit
The new Performance CX generation is now 48% smaller and 25% lighter compare to the previous generation. More compact but no less powerful, the new Bosch Performance CX Generation 4 comes with a maximum power output of 75Nm and 340%. Choose between 5 assist modes or opt for the comfort of the eMTB mode which automatically adapts the assistance like an automatic gearbox does in a car.

***Please note that bike specifications are subject to change without prior notice***

name: Oboz Sapphire Mid Waterproof Hiking Boot - Women's

breadcrumbs.name: Oboz Sapphire Mid Waterproof Hiking Boot - Women's

description:
OBOZ SAPPHIRE MID WATERPROOF HIKING BOOT - WOMEN'S

The women’s-specific Sapphire sports a sculpted fit and a feel that’s tougher than a sneaker and faster than a boot. An EVA midsole, TPU chassis and O FIT insole add up to a vibrant, light-footed mid with B-DRY waterproof protection.

FEATURES

O FIT Insole

Molded to match the specific shape and construction of every pair pf shoes Oboz makes, this purpose-designed technology delivers the kind of fit, feel and performance that’s unmatched in the industry.

Swiftcurrent Midsole

Women’s specific Swiftcurrent midsole provides incredible durability, stability and comfort. The women’s specific cushioning EVA midsole combined with a TPU chassis and ESS plate in the forefoot, which helps prevent stone bruising without inhibiting flex.

Swiftcurrent Outsole

The Swiftcurrent provides incredible durability, stability and comfort with lugs that provide ample traction strolling down Main Street and enough grip under foot to lead you on the trail.

Oboz B-DRY Waterproof

There’s no denying feet sweat and trails can get muddy. There’s also no denying the ability of this proprietary waterproofing system, B-DRY, lets sweat escape while keeping moisture out.

TECH SPECS

Upper Material: Waterproof nubuck leather, Oboz B-DRY waterproof/breathable membrane
Weight: 14.3 oz / 405 g

breadcrumbs.name: CamelBak eddy 14oz Water Bottle W/ Tritan Renew - Kids' (Limited Edition)

description:
CAMELBAK EDDY+ 14OZ BOTTLE WITH TRITAN RENEW - KIDS' (LIMITED EDITION)

An everyday sidekick to lunch boxes everywhere, the Eddy+ Kids water bottle is now made with Tritan Renew, a highly durable and lightweight plastic made with 50% recycled material. In addition to being a feel-good reusable, Eddy + Kids bottles are spill-proof when open and leak-proof when closed - no more soggy backpacks. Just bite to sip and close when finished. The easy carry handle and fun designs make hydrating fun on any adventure. Cap and bottle are odor and stain resistant, dishwasher safe, and free of BPA, BPS, and BPF. Tritan Renew is made using Polyester Renewal Technology, a recycling process that’s more efficient than standard mechanical recycling, producing new material with less demand on finite resources. Fun, functional, sustainable. Recommended for ages 3+.

Flip, Bite, Sip: Drink through straw

name: New Balance 574 Core Shoe - Men's
description:
NEW BALANCE 574 CORE SHOE - MEN'S

‘The most New Balance shoe ever’ says it all, right? No, actually. The 574 might be New Balance's unlikeliest icon. The 574 was built to be a reliable shoe that could do a lot of different things well rather than as a platform for revolutionary technology, or as a premium materials showcase. This unassuming, unpretentious versatility is exactly what launched the 574 into the ranks of all-time greats. As hybrid road/trail design built on a wider last than the previous generation’s narrow racing silhouettes, the 574 offered a uniquely versatile mix of new, different, uncomplicated, rugged, durable, and comfortable that was adopted as a closet staple across the globe. That’s why today, the 574 is synonymous with the boundary defying New Balance style, and worn by anyone.

FEATURES

ENCAP midsole cushioning combines soft foam with a durable polyurethane rim to deliver all-day support
Midsole foam uses approximately 3% bio-based content made from renewable sources to help reduce carbon footprint

TECH SPECS

Rubber outsole with 5% recycled rubber
Suede / mesh upper
Vamp, collar and tongue mesh are 100% recycled polyester

name: Panther Martin Hammered Scented Spinner Lure

breadcrumbs.name: Panther Martin Hammered Scented Spinner Lure

description:
PANTHER MARTIN HAMMERED SCENTED SPINNER LURE

Panther Martin® Scented Lures are an innovative product. The distinction between Panther Martin® Scented Lures and standard Panther Martin® lures is the addition of a proprietary blend of 100% natural oils applied on the hooks. These oils are applied to each hook as a durable finish, giving the hook a distinct garlic or anise scent. These scents are scientifically blended to help the angler to catch more fish than ever before. The revolutionary scent system disperses natural odors which entice targeted species and then encourages a feeding reaction among them. Depending on fishing situations, Panther Martin® Scented Lures will continue to disperse their scent over the course of an average fishing season.

FEATURES

Garlic & Anise Scented Treble Hooks
Hammered Blades Reflect More Light
Powerful Sonic Vibrations Call To Fish
Generously Coated with Long Lasting & Durable Blend of 100% Natural Oil Scents

name: Aetrex Carly Arch Support Shoe - Women's

breadcrumbs.name: Aetrex Carly Arch Support Shoe - Women's

description:
AETREX CARLY ARCH SUPPORT SHOE - WOMEN'S

This fashionable sneaker with arch support is the LIFT you need on long days. They are great for walking and long days on foot! With arch support, memory foam cushioning, a padded heel, and stretchy knit, you will be comfortable on your most active days.

Arch Support
Supporting the arch in the proper place is crucial. Looking at your bare feet, the apex of the arch appears to be in the middle of the foot. An X-ray can confirm the apex is actually further back. The contour, position and height of Aetrex’s unique arch support aligns in the proper place to help support our bodies from the ground up. Aetrex's arch placement is proven to help relieve plantar fasciitis and common heel/arch pain. In additional, it helps to support natural alignment, relieving strain on your knees hips and back.

Metatarsal Pad
Built in forefoot support that helps unload pressure at the metatarsal area and provides cushioning to help relieve discomfort. Cushioning is key to relieving high pressure areas when you stand and walk. Enjoy the pain relief and feel like you're walking on clouds with each and every step.

FEATURES

Arch support helps to stabilize and align feet, relieve common foot pain, & alleviate plantar fasciitis
UltraSky cushioning with High Energy Return
Adjustable laces
Padded heel for extra cushion
Removeable insole
Antimicrobial treated to fight every day odors

TECH SPECS

Upper Material: Stretchy Knit
Midsole Material: UltraSky EVA Foam for comfort & Durability
Heel Height: .7"

name: YETI Tundra 45 Hard Cooler
description:
YETI TUNDRA 45 HARD COOLER

The YETI Tundra 45 combines versatility with durability. This premium cooler is infused with that legendary YETI toughness — a durable rotomolded construction and It's built to last and will keep your contents ice-cold, even in sweltering conditions, like a triple-digit summer day in central Texas. No bowing, cracking, or melting here.

Note: This cooler comes with one Dry Goods basket.

FEATURES

Rotomolded construction for virtually indestructible protection
T-Rex lid latches
NeverFail Hinge System: An interlocking two-pin design that prevents breaking
Bearproof design: Interagency Grizzly Bear Committee (IGBC) approved when used with extra-long shank Master Lock Padlocks
FatWall Design: Extra-thick walls hold up to three inches of insulation for unmatched temperature retention.
PermaFrost Insulation: Pressure-injected polyurethane foam in the walls and lid locks in that just-packed temp.

name: Ultraview Archery UV Button Release
description:
ULTRAVIEW ARCHERY UV BUTTON RELEASE

UV Button is equipped with Ultraview Archery's new ULTRAGLIDE bushing technology resulting in an incredibly low maintenance, smooth, and reliable release. Designed to perfectly fit your hand - UV Button makes every shot comfortable and consistent. It shares the same profile as The Hinge 2, making the switch between both releases seamless. With a wide range of travel and force adjustment, springed d-loop retainment, wrist strap loop, ergonomic contoured knob, rubber bumper silencing system and highly durable Cerakote finish - nothing was spared and no detail overlooked on UV Button.

FEATURES

ULTRAGLIDE - An all-new technology for button releases; ULTRAGLIDE is an advanced self lubricating, internal bushing system that eliminates all unnecessary metal-on-metal contact. This results in an incredibly low maintenance, smooth, reliable and quiet release.
UV Button & Hinge 2 - Both releases have the exact same profile and geometry. This optimizes comfort and consistency when switching releases. As an added bonus, with proper shot execution, you may experience the same point of impact with both releases. Watch this video for achieving the best results: LINK HERE
Convenient Adjustability - Micro-adjust wide ranges of force and travel. The force can be set as feather-light or super-heavy without needing to swap springs.
Springed D-loop Retainment - Allows you to keep UV Button on your string without it falling off, ensuring you’re ready at all times - a must have for all hunters.
Hunting Bracket 3rd Finger - Inspired by The Hunting Bracket, the third finger has a lanyard loop for people who prefer using a wrist lanyard.
Contour Knob - The Contour thumb knob has an ergonomic dished contour with non-slip spiral grooves – ensuring it fits your thumb while creating a tactile repeatable point of reference.
Cerakote - Unmatched durable Smoke Gray and Matte Black Cerakote options available.
Weight - Smoke Gray Aluminum: 3.1oz Matte Black Stainless: 5.6oz

name: Patagonia Houdini Jacket - Women's
description:
PATAGONIA HOUDINI JACKET - WOMEN'S

For practically weightless weather protection on our daily run, hike, or climb, we bring along the Patagonia Houdini Jacket. It's easy to pack down and throw in the pack, a pocket, or on a harness, and keeps us protected from whipping alpine winds and light precipitation. Now made with a completely recycled nylon ripstop that blocks the wind at an ultralight weight, this jacket also features a DWR (Durable Water Repellent) coating that sheds light rain, moderate snow, and whatever mild precipitation you can manage to find in the mountains.

FEATURES

Ultralight and packable shell for windy mountain days
Recycled nylon ripstop blocks the wind on exposed peaks
DWR coating sheds light rain when hiking in drizzly weather
Chest pocket doubles as a stuff sack with a handy carabiner loop
Hood adjusts with one pull to give you quick protection
Full front zipper allows for custom ventilation
Drawcord hem prevents updrafts while climbing
Reflective logo boosts your visibility on nighttime runs

name: Outdoor Products Campfire Genie BBQ Grill And Fire Pit

breadcrumbs.name: Outdoor Products Campfire Genie BBQ Grill And Fire Pit

description:
OUTDOOR PRODUCTS CAMPFIRE GENIE BBQ GRILL AND FIRE PIT

The Campfire Genie is an easy to use BBQ grill and Fire Pit. The grill can be used with wood or charcoal. It's designed to hold logs at the perfect angle to make building your campfire easy and fast starting. The Campfire Genei allows the logs to be elevated off the ground to let a greater amount of air to be pulled into the fire from underneath and accelerate the burn. Once the fire has been started let the logs burn down to coals and attach the round grill for the perfect BBQ. When you are done cooking, all you have to do is remove the grill from the fire pit stand and add logs for an evening by the camp fire.

FEATURES

All in one collapsible BBQ Grll and fire pit stand
Folds flat for compact storage
Large cooking suface holds 16 burgers
Chrome plated cooking grate and body
Includes carry bag, grill and fire pit frame

EASTON GHOST DOUBLE BARREL FASTPITCH BAT 2022 (-10)

IT’S TIME TO MAKE SOME NOISE! The hottest bat in the game is back, now with Sonic Comp Technology. Featuring patented Double Barrel construction, providing the best pop, feel and sound with a massive sweet spot. The Ghost Double Barrel is built with Sonic Comp™, a higher-performing and more durable composite material with the iconic Ghost sound heard on all fields. name: Redington Run Fishing Reel
description:
REDINGTON RUN FISHING REEL

The RUN fly reel was designed for the angler looking for a lightweight reel option with the stopping capabilities of a carbon fiber drag system. It’s durable, non-machinable die-cast aluminum construction features a unique ported arbor on the inner barrel of the spool for increase durability and decreased weight. This large arbor design allows for quick retrieval allowing you to keep the pressure on the fish, no matter how hard the fight is. Its compact carbon fiber drag is smooth and reliable in all types of environments. So, no matter if you’re chasing trout in Montana or find yourself stalking tailing reds during the flood tide, the RUN fly reel is lite on weight not features.

FEATURES

Unmachinable design
Constructed from die-cast aluminum
Ported large arbor design for quick line retrieval
Compact carbon fiber drag that offers smooth stopping power
Easy to adjust recessed drag knob that won’t catch excess line
Push button spool release
Spools are interchangeable with RISE reel
Rounded reel foot for line protection
Twin-molded soft-touch ergonomic handle
Easily converts from left to right hand retrieve
Nylon reel case included
Lifetime warranty

This large arbor design allows for quick retrieval allowing you to keep the pressure on the fish, no matter how hard the fight is. Its compact carbon fiber drag is smooth and reliable in all types of environments. So, no matter if you’re chasing trout in Montana or find yourself stalking tailing reds during the flood tide, the RUN fly reel is lite on weight not features.

FEATURES

  • Unmachinable design
  • Constructed from die-cast aluminum
  • Ported large arbor design for quick line retrieval
  • Compact carbon fiber drag that offers smooth stopping power
  • Easy to adjust recessed drag knob that won’t catch excess line
  • Push button spool release
  • Spools are interchangeable with RISE reel
  • Rounded reel foot for line protection
  • Twin-molded soft-touch ergonomic handle
  • Easily converts from left to right hand retrieve
  • Nylon reel case included
  • Lifetime warranty

name: Sitka Kelvin Aerolite Jacket - Men's
description:
SITKA KELVIN AEROLITE JACKET - MEN'S

In a sea of outdoor specialization, having versatile gear as well is a strength. This lightweight, compressible jacket maximizes warmth while minimizing bulk. Use it for everything from backcountry hunts and off-season scouting trips to everyday life; it slips comfortably under a shell whenever you need an extra shot of warmth. Synthetic PrimaLoft Gold Insulation with Cross Core technology replicates the aesthetics and performance of down insulation, but with warm-when-wet performance.

FEATURES

Synthetic PrimaLoft Gold Insulation with Cross Core technology replicates the warmth and compressibility of down, but with the benefit of warm-when-wet performance
Lightweight insulation (35% recycled) is infused with silica aerogel, a nearly weightless material that’s composed of more than 95% air and acts as additional thermal insulation
DWR finish resists precipitation and prevents face fabric from wetting out
Gusseted stretch cuffs allow for smooth, easy layering and unrestricted shooting
Fitted hood provides low-profile warmth and concealment; doesn’t obstruct peripheral vision
Deep, zippered chest pocket safely stores your valuables

TECH SPECS

Weight: 16 oz.
20-denier polyester face with durable water repellent finish, 20-denier polyester backer

name: Patagonia Arbor 30 Roll Top Backpack
description:
PATAGONIA ARBOR 30 ROLL TOP BACKPACK

This pack is the go-to travel companion, capable of holding anything you may need to stay entertained while you reach your destination. Convenient pockets let us access tech without shuffling the contents of the main compartment, so your essentials stay secure while time flies by. Try using this bag as a daypack; its recycled materials and padded straps offer comfortable day-long wear, and the roll-top opening and water-repellent treatment stop light moisture from penetrating the pack.

FEATURES

Casual pack for commuting to campus or flying cross-country
Roll-top access accommodates a variety of load sizes
DWR finish and tight closure offers water-protection
Crafted from recycled materials for an earth-friendly design
Zip-accessible pocket shelters most fifteen-inch laptops

TECH SPECS

Responsible Collection: Recycled/Repurposed
Material: [face fabric] 600D 100% recycled polyester, PFC-free DWR coating, [lining] 200D 100% recycled polyester, PU coating
Volume: 30L (1831cu in)
Shoulder Straps: padded
Access: roll-top
Pockets: [external] 1 zippered front, 2 stash side, 1 padded laptop, [internal] 1 zippered
Laptop Sleeve: 15in

Manufacturer Warranty: lifetime

name: Salomon Speedcross 6 Trail Running Shoe - Women's

breadcrumbs.name: Salomon Speedcross 6 Trail Running Shoe - Women's

description:
SALOMON SPEEDCROSS 6 TRAIL RUNNING SHOE - WOMEN'S

SPEEDCROSS 6 needs no introductions. Staying true to its legendary roots and trail status, this version is lighter with an even more powerful, grippy connection to the ground and faster mud evacuation. Featuring a revamped upper that’s both functional and fiery, and classic SPEEDCROSS comfort.

FEATURES

Mud Contagrip
Built for maximum grip on loose, soft, rugged, and uneven surfaces, Mud Contagrip uses deep, sharp lugs made from a compound that focuses on adhesion.
EnergyCell+ is a high-rebound midsole compound that provides exceptional energy return along with substantial cushioning and durability.
Recycled material
Materials made from recycled products such as PET bottles or material waste
Anti-debris Mesh
Tight mesh that prevents debris from being trapped between your foot and the footbed.
Ripstop fabric
Woven fabrics, often made of nylon, with reinforcement to resist tearing, ripping and abrasion.
Quicklace
Minimalistic and strong lace for one-pull tightening. Easy-on, easy-off.

LUX PRO MULTI-COLOR BROADBEAM HEADLAMP W/ SPOT LIGHT

The LUXPRO Multicolor broadbeam LED headlamp with a spot light feature is a lightweight and bright headlamp with 300 lumens. This headlamp is versatile with 8 modes: High+ (Spot+Flood), Spot: High and Low, Flood: High, Low, Green, Red, and Hidden Strobe. The dual button operation allows you to easily cycle through the 8 modes. This headlamp has a max run time of 8.5 hours and conveniently operates on 3 AAA batteries which are included. The headband is adjustable, comfortable, and features non-slip stitching for a stable and comfortable fit. Designed with a 45-degree pivoting head to shine light exactly where it’s needed. name: Fischer XJ Sprint Cross Country Ski Boot - Youth

breadcrumbs.name: Fischer XJ Sprint Cross Country Ski Boot - Youth

description:
FISCHER XJ SPRINT CROSS COUNTRY SKI BOOT - YOUTH

A boot with all the advantages and benefits that the youngest skiers need: XJ Sprint. The construction and materials are an ideal balance between practicality, comfort and basic performance. The boot has extra insulation to keep kids comfortable while they learn.

FEATURES

Comfort Guard

Very lightweight, water-repellent insulation material for additional thermal protection in the forefoot and toe-off area.

Easy Entry Loops

Convenient entry loops and wide opening designs ensure boots can be slipped on/off comfortably

Fischer Fresh

Fischer Fresh puts an end to unpleasant odours, giving you long-lasting freshness inside your cross-country ski boot with a pleasant smell and feel inside.

Internal Molded Heel Cap

Anatomical internal heel cup. Very light and individually thermoformable.

Junior fit concept

The right fit for all requirements. Whether designed for the female foot with the comfort or racing version, customized for the feet of young skiers, meeting the comfort requirements of all rounders or for direct power transfer in racing: the Boot concept Fit with special lasts is the answer to all the different needs and morphologies of the various consumer groups.

Lace cover

Lace covers for additional protection against snow and wet conditions and to give you a warm and comfortable feeling

TECH SPECS

Weight: 285g

breadcrumbs.name: Merrell Thermo Kiruna Mid Zip Waterproof Boot - Women's

description:
MERRELL THERMO KIRUNA MID ZIP WATERPROOF BOOT - WOMEN'S

The Merrell Thermo Kiruna Mid Zip Waterproof Boot is the perfect boot for outdoor activities in any season. This waterproof boot keeps your feet warm and dry, whether it’s a cold, wet day in winter or a hot, humid day in summer. The mid-cut design provides extra ankle support, and the breathable mesh lining keeps your feet comfortable and dry. The Vibram outsole provides excellent traction and grip, so you can tackle any terrain with confidence. The Thermo Kiruna also features a durable leather upper, a padded collar and tongue, and a gusseted zipper closure for easy on and off. Whether you’re hiking, walking, or just running errands, the Merrell Thermo Kiruna Mid Zip Waterproof Boot will keep your feet warm, dry, and comfortable.

FEATURES

Embrace the outdoors in the Merrell Thermo Kiruna Mid Zip Waterproof.
Round toe.
Side zip-closure.
Bellows tongue keeps out debris.
Fleece lining for added warmth.
Lightweight.
Heat-reflecting insole radiates body heat back toward the foot.
Merrell Air Cushion in the heel absorbs shock and adds stability.
Branding on heel counter.
Leather and synthetic upper.
Textile lining and insole.
Synthetic outsole.

ATLAS MIKE'S UV GLOW YARN

Atlas Mike’s UV Glow Yarn is a top choice among anglers tying flies and yarn eggs! The unique fat and fluffy Glo Yarn makes great flies! Use with any bait or lure for added color. With 8 colors to chose from, your fly options are endless. Whether you choose your favorite color or your own mix of colors, egg flies are very productive drift bait for catching Trout, Salmon, and Steelhead. Or if you’re really feeling adventurous, you can soak your Glo Yarn in Atlas Mike’s Lunker Oil to attract even more fish!

name: Altra Torin 6 Shoe - Women's
description:
ALTRA TORIN 6 SHOE - WOMEN'S

Versatility and max comfort from the moment you slip your foot in. That's what you'll experience with your updated Women's Altra Torin 6 running shoes. Here's what you need to know. Coming back with the same EgoMax midsole and 28mm stack height as before for that weightless, natural foot-feel you love but now in sleek new color fades that make a statement while you break PR's. Accommodating even those with a wider foot shape, the Torin 6 has leveled up with an evolved heel collar so you can go faster and challenge distances you never imagined.

FEATURES

Running Shoe Support: Neutral runners who don't need a lot of extra support will enjoy the feel of the Women's Altra Torin 6.
Cushion Level: Max Cushion maximizes that plush feel, so every step feels soft and smooth no matter how far you're running.
Midsole Drop: Your Women's Altra Torin 6 has a heel to toe drop of 0 mm.
Shoe Weight: 8.3 ounces
Breathable: The lightweight engineered mesh upper gives you a secure and roomy fit while providing ventilation to keep the foot cool during long-distance running days.
Soft and Springy: The Altra EGO MAX midsole foam provides for a fast yet supportive springy ride.
Locked-In Feel: The Evolved molded heel collar adds to the comfort and fit.
Natural Comfy Fit: With the standard footshape toe box, your feet have more space to sit naturally for enhanced stability and comfort.
Perfect For: Long-distance running, short-distance running and runners who are looking for a zero-drop shoe that can handle any distance. Best for roads and paved trails.

name: Stanislawski Archery OnneX Thumb Release
description:
STANISLAWSKI ARCHERY ONNEX THUMB RELEASE

STAN Onnex releases are designed with legacy features archers must have built into a complete shooting system. Each Onnex handle will allow for the shooter to change between one of the three handle types thumb button, back tension, & resistance seamlessly while maintaining anchor point & peep height

FEATURES

Open hook design for consistent and accurate lateral nock travel
Crisp breaking activation with both independent trigger travel and trigger tension adjustments
Loop retainer allows connection to your bow with the single open hook, while keeping your release connected
Available in multiple sizes to comfortably fit any archers hands
Built on a modular body the release may be shot as a two finger, three finger, or four finger all with one button head screw adjustment with a 5/64" Allen key
Includes two length barrel posts one long and one short as well as two barrel sizes a small and large for perfect hand fit
STAN Trainer Lock feature allows for practice of trigger activation without actually firing

name: Sitka Mountain Pant - Men's
description:
SITKA MOUNTAIN PANT - MEN'S

The Mountain Pant is–hands down–the Swiss knife of big game pants. Designed to deliver the highest performance in the widest range of conditions from chasing September bugles to the last day of the rifle season. As the name implies, the Mountain Pant will be your go-to across multiple seasons and pursuits.

FEATURES

Durable Water Repellent finish resists light precipitation and prevents the face fabric from wetting out.
Articulated Fit: Delivers a maximum range of motion with minimal bulk.
Removable Knee Pads: Removable knee pads offer additional protection whether you’re scrambling through talus in the Northern Rockies, picking your way through cactus in the Sonoran Desert, or field dressing an animal.
GORE OPTIFADE Concealment Subalpine is designed for stalking and ambushing ungulates from ground level in tree-covered and vegetated terrain.

TECH SPECS

Weight: 26.2 oz. // Size: L
Fabric: 4-Way Stretch-Woven Polyester.

name: Mountain House Classic Spaghetti Meat Sauce Freeze Dried Meal

breadcrumbs.name: Mountain House Classic Spaghetti Meat Sauce Freeze Dried Meal

description:
MOUNTAIN HOUSE CLASSIC SPAGHETTI MEAT SAUCE FREEZE DRIED MEAL

What better way to end a long day on the trail or at the office than with a hearty Italian meal? Mountain House Spaghetti with Meat Sauce gives you that wholesome, comforting flavor of Italian cooking in hardly any time at all. Tender spaghetti noodles, hearty chunks of beef, rich marinara sauce - what's there not to love?

FEATURES

Comes in pouch form, making it easy to take this meal on the go. All you need to do is add hot water directly to the pouch, wait several minutes and you'll be ready to enjoy a flavorful, satisfying meal -- no culinary skills required!
Your camping breakfast just got a whole lot tastier. Bring it with you on your next adventure and enjoy!

name: La Sportiva TX4 Shoe - Men's
description:
LA SPORTIVA TX4 SHOE - MEN'S

A leather shoe part of the Traverse X approach series, designed for technical approach routes, via ferrate and hiking: lightweight, comfortable and with a look derived from climbing it is the ideal choice for mountaineers and mountain enthusiasts. Every detail has been studied to guarantee grip, comfort and protection during approach routes and to encourage technical use right up to the base of the wall. TX4 is a sturdy “built to last” boot, thanks to the STB Control System that provides structure and torsion stability. The hard wearing leather uppers have an essential design and are high abrasion resistance thanks to the PU TechLite all-around rand: The Vibram MegaGrip sole with climbing zone at the toe and Impact Brake System at the rear are designed for climbing routes and return trails on technical terrain. The lacing system derives from the Mythos climbing shoe and regulates tension and internal volume in one easy move. Traverse X the ultimate expression of moving in the mountains in comfort, speed and safety.

FEATURES

Mega-Grip Vibram sole with Impact Brake System and climbing zone at the toe
Mythos lacing system
Shock absorbing, injected EVA
The most structured and long lasting boot in the Traverse X series thanks to the leather uppers
STB Control System: the uppers wrap around the midsole at the middle of the boot enhancing stability on traverses providing a snug fit for enhanced comfort and precision
High abrasion resistance and reduced weights thanks to the PU TechLite rand and rubber toe for extra protection, Vibram MegaGrip sole with Impact Brake System at the rear, Trail Bite Heel enhances the downhill grip. Climbing zone at the toe for climbing routes and return trails

breadcrumbs.name: adidas Terrex Free Hiker Gore-Tex 2.0 Hiking Shoe - Men's

description:
ADIDAS TERREX FREE HIKER GORE-TEX 2.0 HIKING SHOE - MEN'S

Hike further. Explore more. Enjoy the view. From thru-hikes to weekend explorations, these lightweight hiking shoes offer next-level comfort and support to extend your range in the mountains. A Boost midsole brings energy to every step to keep you moving on hikes long and short. A GORE-TEX membrane seals out wet conditions while letting your feet breathe as they warm up. The soft, supportive upper and gusseted tongue hug your foot with form-fitting comfort that seals out debris. An internal frame and heel support add the stability to move with confidence over rocky terrain and uneven ground, and the Continental Rubber outsole maintains confident traction whether it's wet or dry.

FEATURES

Regular fit
Lace closure
GORE-TEX membrane
Mesh upper with seamless overlays
External heel clip and EVA stabilization frame
BOOST midsole

TECH SPECS

Weight: 15.5 ounces (size 9)

name: Vans Ultrarange Exo Hi GTX MTE-3 Shoe

breadcrumbs.name: Vans Ultrarange Exo Hi GTX MTE-3 Shoe

description:
VANS ULTRARANGE EXO HI GTX MTE-3 SHOE

The UltraRange EXO Hi GORE-TEX MTE-3 is the continuation of this purpose-built, adventure-based mindset. Not only is this shoe modified to stand up to the journey, but it will keep you comfortable in the most uncomfortable of situations—after all, great surf doesn’t always mean great weather. Armed with the UltraRange EXO MTE-3 outsole featuring All-Trac all-weather rubber, a GORE-TEX internal bootie waterproof membrane, the powerful 3M Thinsulate insulation package, and a triple-density UltraCush EVA midsole with molded heel and toe protection, this shoe is ready to stand in the rain, romp through the mud, and wade through the snow. With this shoe, there is nothing that stands between you and your next great session. It is made with water repellent suede, textile, and synthetic uppers.

FEATURES

Traction: The brand new All-Trac outsole rubber compound with multi-level lug surfacing provides flexible, true all-weather grip that significantly aides in overall traction on all kinds of surfaces.
Thermoregulation: 3M Thinsulate is warm, lightweight, powerful, and thin. The extremely fine microfibers in Thinsulate help to trap air and block heat loss, making for an incredibly efficient insulation while still allowing internal moisture to escape.
Moisture Management: Engineered with a classic internal bootie that allows internal moisture to escape while keeping snow and rain out, the GORE-TEX “GUARANTEED TO KEEP YOU DRY” promise is trusted in any condition.
Comfort And Performance: The triple-density comfort package features a single-density molded open-cell PU sockliner, an UltraRange UltraCush EVA midsole with toe and heel protection, and a molded asymmetrical TPU arch cradle.

name: NEMO Equipment Stargaze Reclining Camp Chair

breadcrumbs.name: NEMO Equipment Stargaze Reclining Camp Chair

description:
NEMO EQUIPMENT STARGAZE RECLINING CAMP CHAIR

The next generation in camp comfort, Stargaze has been re-engineered for even more comfort and stability, with a lower center of gravity and extended fit range. This first-ever swinging and reclining camp chair takes relaxation to a new level. The swinging offers an exciting new sitting experience, with a relaxing motion that is designed for comfort. And when you’re ready to recline, simply lean back to activate the auto-reclining mechanism and enjoy a great view of the stars.

Unlike rocking chairs, this chair is designed for use on any surface, including rocky, sandy, or uneven ground, bringing the relaxation of motion to a host of new environments. The aircraft-grade aluminum is designed to flex while you swing, dynamically suspending you in the air for an entirely new sitting experience. The deep lounge position is hard to beat.

Stargaze has all the little comforts you love, including an adjustable headrest, a no-spill cupholder, and a stash pocket to keep your little things close at hand. This is the chair you’ll want to take to camp, the beach, tailgating, your backyard, or even your kid’s soccer game sidelines. The chair setup is intuitive and easy with just three quick steps, so you can set it up and pack it up into the included padded carrying case quickly. The case comes with a shoulder strap and has room for you to stash your phone and keys. You’ll never think of sitting in the same way!

FEATURES

Chair swings smoothly and gently, with a relaxing motion that is designed for comfort.
A supportive headrest and deep reclining action allow you a full view of the night sky.
A new geometry equates to a lower center of gravity for extended fit range. And unlike rocking chairs, you can swing on any surface, even rocky, sandy, or uneven ground.
Use the auto-reclining feature to find the perfect sitting angle simply by leaning back and shifting your body weight.
The aircraft-grade aluminum suspension frame is sturdier than most camp chairs, yet still packs down quickly and compactly.
The integrated no-spill cupholder keeps your beverages close at hand, and the stash pocket is sized for tablets, keys or your favorite book.
Non-absorbent monofilament mesh is cool and breezy, resists bacteria, withstands sun exposure, and doesn’t retain water.
Setup is intuitive, quick, and easy with just three steps. Anodized pole exterior and red ferrule interior afford precise pole connections for greater stability.
Includes padded carrying case with interior storage pocket for easy portability.

TECH SPECS

Weight: 7 lb , 2 oz / 3.23 kg
Packed Size: 23.5 x 6.5 x 6.5 in / 60 x 17 x 17 cm
Dimensions: 27 x 36 x 44 in / 68 x 92 x 112 cm
Color: Fortress/Goldfinch
Frame: Aluminum
Weight Capacity: 300 lb
Stuff Sack Style: Padded Carrying Case with Adjustable Shoulder Strap

description:
SONA ENTERPRISES BBQ NON-STICK GRILL MAT (2)

When you place the SE Reusable Non-Stick BBQ Grill Mats on top of a cooking grill (either separately or side-by-side), you will instantly have a clean, flat surface to prepare delicious meals for your family and friends at a campsite, park, home, etc. With the entirely non-stick surface, grilling is easier, the food is tastier, and the afterward clean-up is so much faster. name: The North Face Trail Lite 65 Backpack

breadcrumbs.name: The North Face Trail Lite 65 Backpack

description:
THE NORTH FACE TRAIL LITE 65 BACKPACK

A high-spec technical backpack with a sleek design, the Trail Lite Backpack lives for day hikes, tough scrambles and fast-and-light ascents. The generous 65-litre capacity and simplified organisation make it easy to stash essential gear as you go. The proprietary OPTIFIT suspension system ensures a secure fit, while the padded shoulder straps offer plush and breathable comfort when trekking long miles. Outside, there are large stretch side pockets offering quick and easy access to water bottles. Inside, there's a zipped sleeping bag compartment and bottom compression that fits larger items like a tent or sleeping pad. Store jackets, layers and other bulky items into the external stuff-it pocket or clip items onto the daisy chain webbing.

FEATURES

Spacious 65-litre volume
Cinch-top opening is easy to open and close
Massive stretch side pockets easily fit larger water bottles
Hip belt has two secure-zip pockets
External stuff-it pocket fits bulky gear such as jackets or quick-access to snacks and items
Dedicated, zipped sleeping bag compartment
Proprietary OPTIFIT suspension system ensures a comfortable and secure fit
Hip belt has a large padded area to securely and comfortably fit around the hips and uses a dual-density foam for the perfect blend of support and plush cushioning
Shoulder straps offer plush and breathable padding for comfortable use over long miles
Bottom compression secures the bottom of the pack and fits large items such as a tent or sleeping pad
Daisy chain webbing where you can clip on items
Removable top lid allows for separating and organising smaller items
Nylon ripstop fabric is durable yet lightweight
Trekking-pole carry on back of pack
Sternum strap with a whistle buckle

TECH SPECS

Fabric - Boot : 600D Polyester With PU Coating And Non-PFC Durable Water-Repellent (Non-PFC DWR) Finish
Fabric - Body : 210D Recycled Nylon Ripstop With Non-PFC Durable Water-Repellent (Non-PFC DWR) Finish

name: Vans Sk8-Hi MTE-2 Shoe
description:
VANS SK8-HI MTE-2 SHOE

Vans MTE is the byproduct of a lifetime spent outdoors, because the pursuit of your passions isn’t always accompanied by a fair-weather forecast. Rain, sleet, snow, mud, wind—nothing is going to stand between you and your next adventure. It’s why Vans created MTE in the first place.

Made for adventure and advanced levels of day-to-day versatility, the all-new Sk8-Hi MTE-2 packs over 25 years of Vans snowboard boot history and technology into a timeless, trusted style. The MTE-2 feature set includes the new MTE-2 outsole built with All-Trac, an exclusive all-weather rubber compound that offers significantly improved traction and flexibility for all types of weather. The HydroGuard 360-degree waterproof membrane is in place to keep you dry, a PrimaLoft zonal insulation package for cold weather thermoregulation will keep you warm, and the molded UltraCush sockliner with an OrthoLite topsheet has been designed to keep you comfortable. Plus, the durable water repellent-treated leather and textile uppers bring an iconic Vans aesthetic to this uncompromising cold weather comfort.

Whether you find yourself bagging snowcapped peaks or braving a rain-soaked commute, you can set off with confidence knowing every stitch of your equipment is intentionally placed to provide ultimate versatility. After all, it was never about the destination. It’s about the stories you create along your journey.

FEATURES

TRACTION: The brand new All-Trac MTE-2 outsole rubber compound provides flexible, true all-weather grip that significantly aides in overall traction on all kinds of surfaces. THERMOREGULATION: The zonal MTE-2 Primaloft insulation package uses a high-quality microfiber thermal insulation system to mimic the warmth-providing properties of down, keeping you warm without retaining water.
MOISTURE MANAGEMENT: The new MTE-2 HydroGuard 360 package keeps a high waterline for maximum waterproof protection, resulting in a reliable, comfortable, and breathable fit.
COMFORT AND PERFORMANCE: The MTE-2 dual-density comfort package uses a single-density UltraCush molded EVA footbed with an OrthoLite topsheet for enhanced comfort and reduced weight, while also supporting a drier, healthier environment inside your shoe.

description:
SALOMON ADV SKIN 5 RUNNING VEST

Salomon's best-selling vest is a versatile, multi-tasking hydration hero. Designed and fine-tuned for demanding endurance races and runners, ADV SKIN 5 ensures on-the-go access to hydration, long-distance comfort and freedom of movement. This 5L version has an ultra versatile storage unit and is ideal for shorter races and adventures.

Sensifit construction uses stretch, breathable fabrics and lightweight adjustments to optimize fit and stability.
Quick Link sternum strap enables you to adjust your pack quickly on the fly. The elastic makes it easier to breathe when you pick up the pace.
PFC-free

Includes 2 soft flasks, 500 mL

2 expandable front pockets to store essentials you want to access on the go

name: Scientific Anglers Amplitude Smooth Trout Fly Line

breadcrumbs.name: Scientific Anglers Amplitude Smooth Trout Fly Line

description:
SCIENTIFIC ANGLERS AMPLITUDE SMOOTH TROUT FLY LINE

The Amplitude Smooth series of lines are, simply put, the highest-performance smooth fly lines in the world. With up to five times less drag and eight times the durability of traditional lines, this will change the way you look at fly line performance.

There’s a sipper 40 feet away and he looks like he’s eating tricos. The natural rhythms of the rise and the river begin to make sense, so you ready yourself to cast. In that moment, you shouldn’t be thinking about your fly line, because you should trust it implicitly. In that moment, you need the Amplitude Smooth Trout taper. Featuring the unparalleled AST Plus slickness additive, the Amplitude Smooth Trout is designed specifically for precise presentations and those who love dry flies.

FEATURES

Features the revolutionary AST Plus slickness additive for superior shooting ability and increased durability
Excels in medium-to-long distances with dry flies and smaller nymphs; wonderful on glass and bamboo
The best smooth, true-to-grain-weight line for casting small dry flies to picky risers
Designed specifically for chasing trout; also useful for grayling and panfish
Elongated front taper is designed for delicate presentations
For use in moderate and cold climates
Braided multifilament core

SCIENTIFIC ANGLERS AMPLITUDE SMOOTH TROUT FLY LINE

The Amplitude Smooth series of lines are, simply put, the highest-performance smooth fly lines in the world. With up to five times less drag and eight times the durability of traditional lines, this will change the way you look at fly line performance.

There’s a sipper 40 feet away and he looks like he’s eating tricos. The natural rhythms of the rise and the river begin to make sense, so you ready yourself to cast. In that moment, you shouldn’t be thinking about your fly line, because you should trust it implicitly. In that moment, you need the Amplitude Smooth Trout taper. Featuring the unparalleled AST Plus slickness additive, the Amplitude Smooth Trout is designed specifically for precise presentations and those who love dry flies.

FEATURES

  • Designed specifically for chasing trout; also useful for grayling and panfish
  • Elongated front taper is designed for delicate presentations
  • For use in moderate and cold climates

name: CamelBak M.U.L.E. 12 Hydration Pack - Women's
description:
CAMELBAK M.U.L.E. 12 HYDRATION PACK - WOMEN'S

What makes the M.U.L.E. 12 Hydration Backpack redesign so exciting for women? For starters, it's the perfect size, comes with premium hydration and has all the features to make every bike adventure awesome. In addition, it utilizes body-mapping technology, for a tailored fit and excellent cooling. This design supplies an S-curved shoulder harness contoured just right to fit a woman’s body, while providing increased comfort and stability. In addition, the pack shape is thoughtfully designed with a woman’s torso in mind. The trusty CRUX reservoir with Quicklink System delivers easy-access, massive hydration. In addition, CamelBak included smart storage options, with an overflow pocket for an extra layer or wet rain jacket. Finally, there's a removable stability belt for added flexibility and comfort.

Repurpose Gold Sustainability Badge: Made with recycled materials, made with safer chemicals, and designed to preserve resources and diminish disposables.

FEATURES

Air Support back panel is designed with Body Mapping Technology to allow for maximum ventilation on the hottest areas of your back
Magnetic tube trap keeps your tube secure and accessible when you need it
Removable waist strap to add stability when you need it
3D Vent Mesh Harness: Lightweight and breathable with added cargo
Designed for all-day comfort
Helmet Carry: Stow and secure helmet
Stretch overflow pocket so you can quickly stash or shed an extra layer
Integrated carry pockets to keep your tools and repair kit organized

BPA/BPS/BPF free

name: Brooks Cascadia 16 Trail Running Shoe - Women's

breadcrumbs.name: Brooks Cascadia 16 Trail Running Shoe - Women's

description:
BROOKS CASCADIA 16 TRAIL RUNNING SHOE - WOMEN'S

The Brooks Cascadia 16 trail running shoes have the lightweight durability, underfoot support, and reliable outsole grip to keep you steady on every path. These neutral running shoes also feature a protective rock shield plate to help guard against rocks and debris.

FEATURES

Engineered monoloop mesh and 3D Fit Print upper increases breathability and improves drainage for a distraction-free fit.
Mud Guard provides on-the-go protection from trail debris.
Structurally-supportive mid-foot saddle.
Lace-up closure with guard that keeps lace ends secure and tucked away.
Heel pull loop.
Padded tongue and collar.
Soft Element fabric lining offers a great in-shoe feel.
Removable profile sockliner.
Trail-specific Pivot Post System technology supplies stabilizing suspension on both sides of the heel and forefoot and at the toe for a fifth pivot point.
BioMoGo DNA midsole provides long-lasting cushioning, and features an environmentally-friendly build that breaks down 50 times quicker at the landfill, compared to similar midsole materials.
Ballistic Rock Shield protects your foot from rocks and roots on the trail.
Durable rubber outsole featuring TrailTack traction for better grip on a variety of trail surfaces.

TECH SPECS

Support Type: Neutral.
Cushioning: Lightweight, flexible response.
Surface: Trail.
Differential: 8 mm.

name: Vans Old Skool VR3 Shoe
description:
VANS OLD SKOOL VR3 SHOE

This season, some of Vans most iconic Classics have been rebuilt with purposeful choices about the materials they use. Along with uppers made from suede and organic cotton canvas, the Old Skool VR3 utilizes a biobased foam VR3Cush footbed for comfort you can feel good about and the new VR3Waffle outsole that uses natural rubber while still maintaining the grip and durability that Vans has been known for since ’66.

TECH SPECS

Upper material: Made with Suede and Organic Cotton Canvas. By purchasing this product, you are supporting Leather Working Group certified tanneries. Learn more at Leatherworkinggroup.com.
Footbed: The new VR3Cush footbed is made using at least 25% biobased EVA foam partially derived from plants per the ASTM D6866-16 testing standard.
Outsole: The VR3Waffle outsole is made with a proprietary compound containing at least 25% responsibly sourced natural rubber obtained from sources that follow proven sustainable practices with the intention of reducing impacts on the planet. This new natural rubber compound was developed and engineered to maintain the grip and durability Vans is known for (since 66).

description:
GIRO BEVEL SNOW HELMET

The Giro Bevel Snow Helmet offers all-mountain performance at a great price. Built for the adventurous skier or snowboarder, the Bevel is one of the most popular snow helmets. Designed from Giro's anatomic database and improved with rider input with In-Mold Construction, the Bevel has a lightweight feel and low profile shape. name: Big Agnes Fussell UL Quilt
description:
BIG AGNES FUSSELL UL QUILT

This ultralight quilt goes wherever you go. Packing small and weighing in at 1lb, it'll be the envy on thru-hikes, desert camp outs, music festivals and spontaneous couch surfing sessions. The perfect companion for wherever you may lay your head. Insulated with 850 fill power DownTek water-repellent down and featuring snaps that can either close up like a bag or adhere to your pad, this is a warm, technical piece that you'll never forget at home.

FEATURES

Ultralight quilt that is ideal for hut trips, couch surfing, or warm summer nights thru-hiking
Designed as a minimalist quilt that you can tuck around yourself using the top corner hand pockets
Works well as an extra layer over your sleeping bag to provide extra warmth
Integrated snap system creates simplified mummy bag for colder nights
Affix your quilt to your pad to create a secure sleep system using the includes 10 snap patches
Cinch bag tight around shoulders with one-handed cordlock to seal in heat
Minimalistic footbox
Works with any pad size or shape
Storage sack & stuff sack included

TECH SPECS

Ultralight polyester rip-stop shell with a water-repellent finish
Lightweight polyester taffeta lining featuring a wick finish that spreads moisture out for quicker drying and optimal moisture management
850 fill DownTek repels water while maintaining insulating value - bluesign Certified PFC free water repellent chemistry
Includes 10 3M snap patches

name: Mountain House Chicken Teriyaki Rice Freeze Dried Meal

breadcrumbs.name: Mountain House Chicken Teriyaki Rice Freeze Dried Meal

description:
MOUNTAIN HOUSE CHICKEN TERIYAKI WITH RICE

Refuel at the end of a big day of adventure with the mouth-watering Mountain House® Chicken Teriyaki with Rice pouch. This easy-packing, lightweight freeze-dried meal uses chicken, rice, bamboo shoots, mushrooms, and vegetables in a sweet, tangy sauce for a savory meal anywhere you roam. Boasting 240 calories, 12g of protein, and 42g of carbohydrates per serving, this meal is perfect for refueling on the trail. Free of things your body doesn't need, like preservatives, artificial flavors and colors, and gluten, the Mountain House Chicken Teriyaki with Rice provides only what your body needs for a big day of adventure. Simply add hot water directly to the pouch and you'll have a delicious meal ready to eat in less than 10 minutes – and not a single pot or pan to scrub when you're through!

FEATURES

Easy-to-pack, lightweight, and delicious freeze-dried meal
240 calories, 12g of protein, and 42g of carbs per serving
Fast and easy to make – just add hot water
Preservative-, artificial-flavor-, and gluten-free
Includes 2 servings per pouch
Recyclable through TerraCycle

name: Feedback Sports Pro-Elite Repair Stand
description:
FEEDBACK SPORTS PRO-ELITE REPAIR STAND

Whether you're on the go or working from home, the Feedback Sports Pro-Elite Repair Stand lets you be the ultimate bike mechanic. Able to hold up to 85 lbs and an adjustable stand height reaching up to 71 inches tall, you can make repairs from any angle thanks to 360° rotation. And if you're on the road, don't worry about too much weight, because the Feedback Sports Pro-Elite Repair Stand folds into a compact size and weighs just 12 lbs.

FEATURES

Patented seatpost clamp features ratchet-action closure, micro-adjustability and push-button release
360° rotating clamp design provides easy access to any part of your bicycle
Frame clamp positions from 42"-71" (107-180cm) in height
Rubber clamp jaws protect expensive components
Micro-adjustment confidently secures virtually any bike
Anodized 6061 T6 aluminum construction is ultralight, corrosion-resistant, and durable
Stiff tripod base and rubber-coated end caps create ultimate stability even on uneven surfaces
Total load capacity of 85lbs (39kg) accommodates service on road, cyclocross, mountain bikes, and electric bikes
Portable and compact construction creates a remarkably small folded footprint of 5" x 7.8" x 46" (12.7 x 20 x 117cm)
Available travel bag is water-resistant, durable, and padded to protect your stand and your other equipment
Quick-release fittings make setup and storage fast and easy

TECH SPECS

Work Height: 42" - 71" (107-180cm)
Clamp Opening: up to 2.6" (6.6cm)
Folded Size: 5" x 7.8" x 46" (12.7 x 20 x 117cm)
Weight: 12.6 lbs (5.kg)
Load Capacity: 85 lbs (39kg)
Material: Anodized aluminum

name: The North Face Dolomite One Double Sleeping Bag

breadcrumbs.name: The North Face Dolomite One Double Sleeping Bag

description:
THE NORTH FACE DOLOMITE ONE DOUBLE SLEEPING BAG

If you've found someone to share your sleeping bag with, you're halfway there. The versatile Dolomite One Double is Heatseeker Eco-insulated and can configure for comfort in a range of climates. The top layer features 50-degree-rated synthetic insulation for versatile use in warmer weather, and the mid layer features 30-degree-rated synthetic insulation for cool nights in the outdoors. Together, the two layers can pair to get a 15-degree bag - that's called maximum versatility.

FEATURES

Double size offers plenty of room for you and your partner
Two layers of insulation offer three temperature options in one
Zippers open from the bottom to allow for extra ventilation
Watch pocket included
Rectangular shape is super roomy for the ultimate comfortable experience
Comfortable fleece lining on the mid-layer is super soft and makes you want to slide right in

TECH SPECS

Temp Rating: 15°F, 30°F, 50°F

name: Redington Benchmark Wading Boot
description:
REDINGTON BENCHMARK WADING BOOT

Not all wader boots need to look and feel like you borrowed Frankenstein’s boots for the weekend. A simplistic, lightweight approach is the foundation of our new BENCHMARK WADING BOOTS. The quick drying, abrasion-resistant upper is strong enough to hold up in technical wading situations and designed to dry out before your flight home. Whether you’re wading into the river for the first time or booking your next destination trip, the BENCHMARK WADING BOOTS will surprise any angler with its simplistic, thoughtful design.

FEATURES

Wide sole design for enhanced comfort and increased stability
Lightweight, shock-absorbing EVA midsole for all-day comfort
Rubber rand for abrasion resistance, durability, and foot protection
Improved drainage works to reduce water-log and maintain lightweight design
Corrosion-resistant lace hooks at the top of the boot for easy lacing
Webbing pull-loops for easy-on
Available felt or sticky rubber sole options
Sticky rubber sole for secure traction both in and out of the water
Felt sole for maximum underwater traction
Stud compatible. Redington recommends up to 3/8-inch studs for sticky rubber soles and up to 1/2-inch studs for felt soles

The water-repellent Green Kazoo Eco is a highly compressible and lightweight zero-degree bag made with shell fabric and insulation that are both 100% recycled. With a toasty 700-fill down and a fully insulated hood, it'll be your best friend after a hard day's hike.

Highly compressible, recycled 700 fill down retains loft and warmth season after season
Fully insulated hood with a cinch collar helps seal out chilly breezes and helps keep your head warm

Compression stuff sack included

name: Exped FlexMat Plus
description:
EXPED FLEXMAT PLUS

FlexMat Plus is the thickest, most-comfortable closed-cell mat available. With 1.5” of air-trapping Flex-Cells, it is highly versatile for stand-alone use and will increase warmth and puncture protection for inflatable mats. Because R-values are additive, FlexMat Plus’s R-value of 2.2 can boost a 3-season sleeping mat to 4-season efficiency. The folding form is quick to deploy and ensures a tidy load when attached to a backpack, bike or kayak.

FEATURES

High-quality, nontoxic microcellular IXPE foam is extremely lightweight and durable, and it maintains the Flex-Cell structure for years of hard use
An array of air-trapping Flex-Cells creates a thick, warm, supportive sleep surface, and they nestle inside one another when the mat is folded, minimizing packed size
Multiple rectangular segments fold against one another into a compact, easily packable shape
Warmth-to-weight ratio is extremely high, making the FlexMat Plus an essential addition to any sleep system across all seasons
FlexMat adds substantial insulation, durability and moisture resistance to inflatable sleeping mats when layered beneath
Winter Mode—folded in half and doubled in thickness, FlexMat Plus increases insulation and cushioning under the torso; excellent for winter camping
Pillow Mode—with the first several segments stacked one atop the other, an elevated, customized pillow section can be created, supporting the head and neck

TECH SPECS

Temperature: 32 °F
R-Value: 2.2
Materials: Closed-cell IXPE foam, DWR free

name: Feetures Elite Light Cushion No Show Tab Sock

breadcrumbs.name: Feetures Elite Light Cushion No Show Tab Sock

description:
FEETURES ELITE LIGHT CUSHION NO SHOW TAB SOCK

To Roam is to wander with purpose. Explore a trail, a pose, a time of being awake that few others dare. Get out and Roam in a sock engineered with anatomical design and Targeted Compression, providing a Custom-Like Fit and reduced risk of blisters, plus a Light Cushion for added impact protection.

These socks are elite, meaning they have enhanced fit and feel. If you’re looking for the best performance sock on the planet, the Elite socks have it all. They feature Targeted Compression, zone specific compression where you need it most for superior comfort and support. As a result they have an anatomical design, meaning they conform to the left and right structure of the foot.

FEATURES

Targeted Compression and anatomical design provide an unmatched Custom-Like Fit.
High density cushioning provides cushioned comfort without the bulk.
Anatomical design enhances fit, delivering maximum comfort and protection by eliminating blisters.
The Perfect Toe. (No irritating toe seam.)
No Show Tab height sits below the ankle for maximum versatility.
Wicks moisture to keep feet cool and dry, while providing superior durability.

TECH SPECS

96% Nylon, 4% Spandex

name: Terramar Sports 2.0 Thermolator Performance Pant - Men's

breadcrumbs.name: Terramar Sports 2.0 Thermolator Performance Pant - Men's

description:
TERRAMAR SPORTS 2.0 THERMOLATOR PERFORMANCE PANT - MEN'S

The Thermolator Pant is the ideal piece for all day warmth and comfort while being out in the elements. These versatile thermal long johns feature an ultra-soft, mid-weight fabric utilizing Terramar's ClimaSense Thermoregulation Technology that automatically adjusts to your body temperature.

It does this by trapping air to maintain warmth when your body starts to cool down. When your aerobic activity increases and your skin temperature rises, the fabric allows moisture vapor to escape to maintain comfort.

Whether skiing, mountaineering, biking, snowshoeing, winter running or just enjoying the outdoors during the winter, Thermolator is functional performance at its best! The Thermolator Pant goes perfectly with the Men’s Thermolator Crew and other pieces from the Thermolator collection.

FEATURES

Ultra-soft brushed fabric surface traps air to maintain warmth
UPF rating 25+ and mid-weight warmth
Flatlock seams and 4-way stretch and gusseted panels for ease of movement
Odor locking technology inhibits the growth of bacteria that causes odor
4-Way Stretch moves naturally with your body in all activities

TECH SPECS

28.25" inseam, ankle-length fit
86% Waterless Dye Polyester, 14% Spandex
descriptionHtml:
TERRAMAR SPORTS 2.0 THERMOLATOR PERFORMANCE PANT - MEN'S

The Thermolator Pant is the ideal piece for all day warmth and comfort while being out in the elements. These versatile thermal long johns feature an ultra-soft, mid-weight fabric utilizing Terramar's  ClimaSense Thermoregulation Technology that automatically adjusts to your body temperature.

It does this by trapping air to maintain warmth when your body starts to cool down. When your aerobic activity increases and your skin temperature rises, the fabric allows moisture vapor to escape to maintain comfort.

Whether skiing, mountaineering, biking, snowshoeing, winter running or just enjoying the outdoors during the winter, Thermolator is functional performance at its best! The Thermolator Pant goes perfectly with the Men’s Thermolator Crew and other pieces from the Thermolator collection.

FEATURES

  • Ultra-soft brushed fabric surface traps air to maintain warmth
  • UPF rating 25+ and mid-weight warmth
  • Flatlock seams and 4-way stretch and gusseted panels for ease of movement
  • Odor locking technology inhibits the growth of bacteria that causes odor
  • 4-Way Stretch moves naturally with your body in all activities

TECH SPECS

  • 28.25" inseam, ankle-length fit
  • 86% Waterless Dye Polyester, 14% Spandex

name: Redington Tilt Euro Nymph Fly Reel

breadcrumbs.name: Redington Tilt Euro Nymph Fly Reel

description:
REDINGTON TILT EURO NYMPH FLY REEL

Redington knows what keeps you up at night. It’s that feeling of your line going tight and the bend in your rod. It’s the drive to be the top rod, whether it’s at your local comp or just another day out fishing with your friends. The TILT Euro Nymph Fly Reel was designed to give you the unfair advantage you have been looking for. Redington incorporated three one-ounce removable weights that will allow anglers to dial in any rod and find that perfect balance. The TILT features a fully machined, full-frame narrow large arbor design, which prevents narrow comp line from slipping in between the frame and the spool, with the capability of quick line retrieval. At the heart of this design is a carbon fiber drag system that will quickly put the brakes on any fish, so you quickly get it in the net and your flies back into the water. So enjoy the unfair advantage of the TILT reel and rest easy tonight.

FEATURES

CNC machined, anodized 6061-T6 aluminum design with quick release spool
Smooth, compact carbon fiber drag system
Full frame design
Narrow ultra large arbor design for maximum line retrieval
Includes three one ounce removable weights allowing for the perfect balance of any rod
Rounded reel foot for line/leader protection when stowed
Includes 2MM Allen Wrench

TECH SPECS

2/5 Specs

Line Size: 2-5
Reel Diameter: 4
Yards/lbs: 100/20
Reel Weight: 5.7oz

Their streamlined design is centered on your leader for balanced casting, and they float more weight than the current leading brand.

Recommended for 5X Tippet or heavier
Does not kink the line
Float as much or more weight than the current leading brand
Smooth surface developed to repel water and dirt, and create less drag while casting
Made with a Biodegradable additive that accelerates biodegradation with prolonged exposure in natural environments, not in normal use
Strike indicator top and bottom colors can be mixed or matched by anglers for optimal visibility
Comes in a pack of three: orange, white, pink

name: Coates Eland Fairway 3 Wood - Women's
description:
COATES ELAND FAIRWAY WOOD - WOMEN'S

Coates was inspired by the Eland driver to design a fairway metal that provides distance and control when it's most needed. The Eland Fairway Metal features an ultra-thin titanium face that seamlessly transfers energy into the ball upon impact, resulting in maximum ball contact and confidence in distance and direction control from any lie. With 15 and 18 degree options, the Eland Fairway Metal effortlessly fills the gap between a player's driver and long irons, making it both easy-to-hit and consistent. Unlike traditional painted finishes, each Eland Fairway metal is coated with a chip, scratch, and rust-resistant finish using the pressure vapor deposition method, reducing drag through grass and eliminating glare during play with its elegant satin black look. Coates believes in customization for each player's game and offers multiple shaft options to complete your Eland Fairway Wood.

name: Osprey 1.5L Hydraulics LT Reservoir
description:
OSPREY 1.5L HYDRAULICS LT RESERVOIR

Osprey’s Hydraulics LT 1.5L Reservoir by Hydrapak is made for light and fast activities where weight and balance are critical. Twin-welded chevron baffles stabilize the water and maintain a flat profile. The streamlined design allows for easy loading into internal hydration sleeves. Thoughtful design makes filling, cleaning and most importantly staying hydrated on the trail easier than ever. All parts are BPA-free, phthalate-free, lead-free, guaranteed. All materials are certified food safe according to FDA and EU regulations.

FEATURES

Twin Baffles - Twin-welded chevron baffles stabilize the water and maintain a flat profile.
Slide-Seal - Easy Slide-Seal top opening, seals watertight and provides wide access for easy filling and cleaning
Pour Shield - Pour shield extends the collar to ease filling in shallower sinks and control pouring into pots or bottles
Carry Handle - Carry handle allows easy reservoir management and filling
Magnetic Bite Valve - Magnet clip attaches to the reservoir hose and pairs with the included sternum strap magnet for easy water access and hose management
Hydrapak Blaster - Hydrapak Blaster bite valve offers fast, smooth water flow with a 1/4 twist on/off switch
QuickConnect System - The QuickConnect system allows easy removal/filling of the reservoir and filtering in the backcountry

TECH SPECS

Dimensions: 15H X 8W X 2D In
Weight: 0.37 Lbs

name: Easton Easton 6.5mm – Hunter Classic Arrow
description:
EASTON EASTON 6.5MM – HUNTER CLASSIC ARROW

Hunting accuracy for shooter confidence is the cornerstone of Easton 6.5 arrows. The 6.5 uses proprietary Acu-Carbon™Uniform Spine process. Acu-Carbon™ is a continuous-fed, single-die manufacturing method that results in the most reliable tolerances and eliminates the need for the spine-alignment and weight sorting. Easton’s Acu-Carbon™ production line produces the most consistent spine and weight from dozen to dozen and lot to lot—year in and year out. This benefits the bowhunter with truer flight and pinpoint accuracy in the field.

Easton, the top name in archery since 1922, has announced the new 6.5 hunting arrow line available now for immediate delivery. The Easton 6.5MM™ arrows are USA-made shafts that offer the highest level of accuracy available to bowhunters today all at price points to fit virtually any budget.

The Easton 6.5 includes NEW 6.5MM inserts that are made using a 4X-larger shoulder to add strength and boost valuable FOC.

FEATURES

·6.5MM Inserts included—precision machined component has four-times larger shoulder. Strengthens the broadhead/arrow interface and boosts F.O.C. (23 grains)
·Microlite Nocks—shortens the critical distance between the shaft and bowstring for improved alignment and reduced weight.
·Acu-Carbon™ Uniform Spine USA Manufacturing Process for the highest level of accuracy.
·Bully™ Vane Fletching—stiffer material for superior control and quiet arrow flight.
·Available in three models: Match Grade +/- .001”, Hunter Classic +/- .003”, and Bowhunter +/- .006”

name: Fischer XC Comfort Pro Ski Boot - Women's

breadcrumbs.name: Fischer XC Comfort Pro Ski Boot - Women's

description:
FISCHER XC COMFORT PRO SKI BOOT - WOMEN'S

Comfort and control continues to be the focus of the best-selling Comfort Pro. The breathable Triple-F membrane sheds snow for a warm, dry boot, while the molded heel and Velcro power strap team up for improved stability and power transfer.

FEATURES

Comfort Guard

Very lightweight, water-repelling insulation material for additional thermal protection in the forefoot and toe area.

Easy Entry Loops

Practical entry loops and wide-opening designs guarantee that boots can be put on/taken off comfortably.

Fischer Fresh

Fischer Fresh puts an end to unpleasant odours, giving you lasting freshness inside the cross country skiing boot with a pleasant smell and feeling inside.

Fischer Speed Lock

New, revolutionary quick lock with minimum size and weight. Simply pull the laces tight , that's it! The system is safe and reliable.

Injected Exterior Heel Cap

Good heel cradling and robust protection all in one: exterior heel cap for even better power transfer.

Lace Cover

Lace covers for additional protection against the snow and wet conditions and to give you a comfortable warm feeling.

Sport Fit Concept

The right fit for all requirements. Whether it's shaped for the female foot with the comfort or race version, customised for the feet of young skiers, meeting the comfort requirements of all-rounders or for direct power transfer in racing: the Boot Fit Concept with special lasts is the answer to all the different needs and morphologies of the various consumer groups.

Thermo Fit

Thermally formable foam cushioning with outstanding thermal insulation – a perfect fit for the individual shape of the foot. Heat boot to max. 85°C (185°F) in oven. Step in with socks and tighten laces. Foam adapts automatically. Allow 7-10 min of cooling time.

Triple F Membrane

Special membrane ensures that conditions inside the boot are perfect: dry, warm and breathable.

TURNAMIC Performance

Robust sole for sporty skiing style. The flat construction enables a longer gliding phase through easier balance. Flex grooves and soft sole flex support the smooth kick. The profile is non-slip and and self-cleaning. 2K-Desmopan material blend for enhanced skiing performance.

Velcro Strap

Fastening element for cuffs and instep straps, easy to handle and adjust.

TECH SPECS

Sole: TURNAMIC Performance
Sole Flex: soft
Weight (g): 485g

description:
STANCE COTTON QUARTER ANYTHING SOCK

With a plush medium cushion and soft combed cotton blend, these durable socks provide a secure fit that'll keep you going all day.

FEATURES

Landing at just above your ankle, these socks are the mid-point between no show and crew heights
The old-school standard when it comes to comfort, Stance's classic combed cotton blend delivers premium all-day breathability in a variety of versatile constructions

Infiknit specifically targets high-friction areas for an all-new super tough standard in durability. By adding some serious muscle to both the heel and toes, Infiknit guarantees a longer, stronger lifespan than your typical sock construction

The Ultra-Sil Dry Bag won the sought-after Backpacker Editors' Choice award in 2006 and remains the ideal dry bag for backpacking and travel. Made with lightweight, waterproof bluesign approved 30D Ultra-Sil fabric featuring Cordura yarns, it's the perfect choice to organize your gear inside your backpack or duffle like a pro.
